NK005(ca)003:0: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba rigs
NK005(ca)003:1: bsdus pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen 'dod 'jo zhes bya
NK005(ca)003:3: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba rigs
NK005(ca)003:4: bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i sgrub thabs bde chen
NK005(ca)003:6: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:7: mchog tu mi 'gyur bde ba chen po'i dngos //
NK005(ca)003:8: mtshan ma'i rtog pa kun las rnam grol yang //
NK005(ca)003:9: ye shes sgyu ma rigs drug dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK005(ca)003:10: 'khor lor snang mdzad rdo rje sems dpar 'dud //
NK005(ca)003:11: spros bral de bzhin nyid kyi gnas lugs gang //
NK005(ca)003:12: rnam 'gyur dbyibs kyi rnal 'byor brda nyid las //
NK005(ca)003:13: don mtshon byed pa'i sgrub thabs bde chen gyis //
NK005(ca)003:20: re zhig rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK005(ca)003:21: dang po las can rnal 'byor pas //
NK005(ca)003:22: rgyu rkyen lam dang 'bras bu dang //
NK005(ca)003:23: rgya chen thun mong spyod pa spyad //
NK005(ca)003:24: thams cad cig char rdzogs pa'i tshul //
NK005(ca)003:26: rten gyi sgrub pa po dang po'i las can gyi dbang du byas te /
NK005(ca)003:27: lam thun mong pas rgyud sbyangs ba dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs shing dam tshig la gnas pa /
NK005(ca)003:28: gsang ba'i cho ga la mkhas pa sogs kyi snod du rung ba'o //
NK005(ca)003:31: rjes kyi bya ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:33: dang po bya ba'i sngon 'gro ni /
NK005(ca)003:34: phun sum tshogs pa'i gnas khang mdzes par brgyan /
NK005(ca)003:35: bris sku dang mchod gtor la sogs pa nye bar
NK005(ca)003:36: mkho ba'i yo byad thams cad tshogs par bsham mo
NK005(ca)003:37: // gnyis pa sngon 'gro gtor ma ni /
NK005(ca)003:38: gtor ma rgyan ldan bshams la byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK005(ca)003:39: s+th+aa na pa ti k+she tra p+aa lany+tsa na mahsarba
NK005(ca)003:40: ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo sogs gsum gyis bsngosa la
NK005(ca)003:41: / gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu //
NK005(ca)003:44: bdag nyid rdo rje rta mchog tu gyur pa'i thugs
NK005(ca)003:45: ka nas khro bo'i sprin spros pas bgegs dang log
NK005(ca)003:46: par 'dren pa thams cad bskrad cing mtshams bcad par
NK005(ca)003:47: bsam la / yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK005(ca)003:48: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK005(ca)003:49: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK005(ca)003:50: gsang ba nyan par mi dbang ba'i //
NK005(ca)003:51: bgegs dang 'byung po thams cad kun //
NK005(ca)003:52: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK005(ca)003:53: h+aum mdzad kyi yan lag bzhi pa las /
NK005(ca)003:54: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK005(ca)003:55: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:56: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis //
NK005(ca)003:57: rtag tu brlag cing phung bar 'gyur //
NK005(ca)003:58: badz+ra dz+wa la ram yam kham tsakra bi shwa h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:59: ces drag tu brjod pas mtshams bcad /
NK005(ca)003:60: gsum pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:61: rang nyid skad cig gis dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK005(ca)003:62: skur gyur pa'i lag pa g.yas par nyi ma'i dkyil
NK005(ca)003:63: 'khor drug gi steng du h+aum hi h+r+aihtram h+aam rnams
NK005(ca)003:64: las / rdor sems rnam snang khrag 'thung dang //
NK005(ca)003:65: gar dbang nyi ma rta mchog go //
NK005(ca)003:66: lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i dkyil 'khor drug gi steng du a yig dkar po drug las /
NK005(ca)003:67: bzang mo spyan ma kro d+hi ma //
NK005(ca)003:68: gos dkar m+aa ma k+ai sgrol ma //
NK005(ca)003:69: lce la na mastu bud+d+he b+h+yah zhes pas mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:72: bdag nyid sems dpa' sum brtsegs su gyur /
NK005(ca)003:75: mdzod spu nas spros pa'i 'od zer gyis srid pa gsum sbyangs /
NK005(ca)003:76: rdo rje gsum gyi go 'phang la bkod /
NK005(ca)003:77: rang gi tshangs bug tu zhugs shing thim /
NK005(ca)003:79: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad spyan drangs par bsam la /
NK005(ca)003:80: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra sa m+aa dzah e h+ye hi
NK005(ca)003:81: b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri
NK005(ca)003:82: sh+yahoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:83: zhes spyan drangs pa nam mkhar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)003:84: ma h+aa sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:85: lan gnyis kyis chu gnyis phul /
NK005(ca)003:87: bgegs thams cad bshig cing srung ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad /
NK005(ca)003:89: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya wa k+tsit+ta b+han+d+ha nam ka ro mi /
NK005(ca)003:91: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na //
NK005(ca)003:92: rdo rje rin chen bla na med //
NK005(ca)003:93: rdo rje chos ni glur blangs pas //
NK005(ca)003:94: rdo rje las kun byed par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)003:95: zhes pa'i glu sngon du btang nas /
NK005(ca)003:98: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:100: badz+ra a ha ra h+r+aih na mahsarba ta th+aa ga
NK005(ca)003:101: te b+h+yo a lang+ka ra pa na bee h'u s+w+aa
NK005(ca)003:102: h+aa / b+h+yo d+h+yam rat+na me g+ha s+pha ra na h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:104: na mahsarba pany+tsa r+aa sa ya na a mri te h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:106: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:108: bla ma ku ku r+aa dza'i cho ga lnga pa las /
NK005(ca)003:110: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la yang //
NK005(ca)003:111: rnam kun btud de skyabs mchi zhing //
NK005(ca)003:113: sdig pa las ni ldog bgyi zhing //
NK005(ca)003:114: bsod nams thams cad yongs su bzung //
NK005(ca)003:115: lus can rnams kyi bsod nams dag /
NK005(ca)003:116: kun la rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK005(ca)003:117: bdag ni lus btud thal sbyar nas //
NK005(ca)003:118: gsang ba'i theg chen bshad pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:119: 'gro gnas bar du bzhugs slad du //
NK005(ca)003:120: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams la gsol //
NK005(ca)003:121: de ltar bgyis pa'i bsod nams gang //
NK005(ca)003:122: bdag gis bgyis dang ma bgyis gang //
NK005(ca)003:123: des ni sems can thams cad kyang //
NK005(ca)003:124: bla med byang chub gnas thob shog /
NK005(ca)003:126: yi ge brgya pa'i mthar +aahh+aum zhes btags pa bzla /
NK005(ca)003:127: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis gshibs pa'i mthe bong bsgrengs nas g.yob /
NK005(ca)003:128: rdo rje thal mo smad mi drag par lan gsum brdab cing /
NK005(ca)003:129: badz+ra gats+tsha muh badz+ra tush+ya hoh zhes tshogs zhing gshegs su gsol /
NK005(ca)003:130: sems can bde dang ldan gyur cig /
NK005(ca)003:131: sdug bsngal kun dang bral bar shog /
NK005(ca)003:132: bde dang rtag tu mi 'bral zhing //
NK005(ca)003:133: chos kun mnyam nyid rtog par shog /
NK005(ca)003:134: ces tshad med bzhi bsgom ste yul mchog dman la tshogs bsags pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:135: bzhi pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:136: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK005(ca)003:137: stong pa'i ngang las pad nyi la h+aum las sna tshogs rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:138: de las 'od 'phros rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba
NK005(ca)003:139: d+r+wa ba gur bla re phyi rol bskal pa'i me
NK005(ca)003:140: dpung 'bar ba'i dbus su bdag nyid dpal rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:141: sems dapa'o // dpung pa gnyis rdo rje bcings pa'i tshul du bsnol te /
NK005(ca)003:142: se gol gtogs ba'i sgra dang /
NK005(ca)003:143: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahsangasa rgyas thams cad sad par byas
NK005(ca)003:144: te 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad til gyi gang
NK005(ca)003:145: bu bzhin du gang bar bzhugs pa rnams kyis /
NK005(ca)003:146: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK005(ca)003:147: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK005(ca)003:148: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo yis //
NK005(ca)003:149: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:150: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:151: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
NK005(ca)003:152: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis //
NK005(ca)003:153: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK005(ca)003:154: zhes bka' bgro ba mdzad nas gcig tu 'dus pa bdag nyid la thim par gyur /
NK005(ca)003:155: h'u ring po gsum sna bug nas brjod /
NK005(ca)003:156: rang nyid khro bo thams cad kyi rgyal po dpal he ru kar gyur pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:157: sku mdog sngon po rab tu khros pa'i rtsa zhal mthing nag 'bar ba chen po'i 'od zer can /
NK005(ca)003:158: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rgyab ser ba ste zhal bzhi pa /
NK005(ca)003:159: phyag brgyad kyi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje dang
NK005(ca)003:160: kha t+w+aam ka dril bu gsil ba dang bcas pa
NK005(ca)003:161: / gnyis pas lcags kyu dang zhags pa /
NK005(ca)003:162: gsum pas ral gri dang thod pa /
NK005(ca)003:163: bzhi pa gnyis kyis phyag mtshan 'di dag yan lag bzhi pa las so //
NK005(ca)003:165: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la rdzogs shing /
NK005(ca)003:166: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma gcer bu thod pa
NK005(ca)003:167: dang ba dan gsum pa'i phyag rgya can gyis 'khyud
NK005(ca)003:168: pa / de'i thugs ka nas khro bo /
NK005(ca)003:170: phyogs bcu'i bgegs tshogs thams cad bkug ste pho mo
NK005(ca)003:171: bsnol mar nyi ma la myos shing 'khod par gyur
NK005(ca)003:174: gri h+na pa ya gri h+na pa ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:175: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga w+aan bid+y+aa r+aa dza h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:176: in+d+ra ya dzah ya ma y+aa dzah ba ru na
NK005(ca)003:177: ya dzah ku be r+aa ya dzah ag+na ya dzah
NK005(ca)003:178: ni ri t+ya ya dzah b+hi ram p+aa ya dzah
NK005(ca)003:179: i sha n+aa ya dzah tsan+d+ra ya dzah su ti
NK005(ca)003:180: ta ya dzah e ra pa ta yee dzah zhes
NK005(ca)003:181: bgegs so so'i ming sngags brjod cing dran pas gdan
NK005(ca)003:182: gsal btab / slar yang rang gi snying ga nas khro bo bcu spros /
NK005(ca)003:183: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:184: badz+ra kro d+hi ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:185: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:186: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum tshin+da tshin+da h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:187: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:188: badz+ra kro d+ha ar+ya +aa tsa la h+aum ban+d+ha ban+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:189: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum tish+tha tish+tha h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:190: badz+ra kro d+ha tre lokya bi dza ya h+aum b+hin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:191: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum gardza gardza h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:192: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:193: thams cad kyang sku mdog mthing nag nag dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK005(ca)003:194: g.yas gsum rdo rje ral gri tho ba /
NK005(ca)003:195: g.yon gsum thod khrag zhags pa lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:196: smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pa can du gyur /
NK005(ca)003:197: de nas khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba tho ba thogs pa sprul te /
NK005(ca)003:198: g+ha g+ha g+ha ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK005(ca)003:200: k+ai li ya k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam phata /
NK005(ca)003:201: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra d+h+aa ra adz+ny+aa pa ya ti
NK005(ca)003:202: sarba big+h+n+aam k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la
NK005(ca)003:203: ya h+aum phata / ces khro bo rnams phyogs bcu'i
NK005(ca)003:204: bgegs la phur bu'i tshul du btab pas de rnams
NK005(ca)003:205: kyi lus phug ste g.yo 'gul med par byas nas
NK005(ca)003:206: ya h+aum phata / / 'od zer rnon po 'khrug cing 'bar bas kyang bgegs thams cad bsregs /
NK005(ca)003:207: rdo rje'i gur gyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bcu
NK005(ca)003:208: pa'i rtsibs rnams la khro bo rnams bzhugs shing sprul
NK005(ca)003:209: pa dang yang sprul nam mkha' gang bas bgegs thams
NK005(ca)003:210: cad bsrung ba'i las mdzad par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)003:211: don dam par bsrung bya srung byed sogs mtshan ma'i
NK005(ca)003:212: dmigs yul dang bral ba'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog
NK005(ca)003:213: pa ste kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i srung 'khor
NK005(ca)003:214: lo // lnga pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:215: sngar gyi tshogs bsag gi khongs su bsdus kyang rung mod /
NK005(ca)003:216: spro na tshogs zhing sngar bzhin sad pa'i spyan sngar
NK005(ca)003:217: bshags sdom gyi bsam pa drag pos thal mo sbyar
NK005(ca)003:220: gsang ldan rdo rje che ge mos //
NK005(ca)003:221: rdo rje slob dpon dmod 'gal zhing //
NK005(ca)003:222: lha dang mched la 'khus pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:223: sngags dang phyag rgya spangs pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:224: snod min gsang ba bsgrags la sogs //
NK005(ca)003:225: gnyis gsum nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:226: yan lag cha shas nyams las 'das //
NK005(ca)003:227: 'gyod sems nges pas bshags par bgyi //
NK005(ca)003:228: na mahk+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta sarba p+aa pam bi shud+d+he h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:230: spro na spyi bshags kyang sbyar ro //
NK005(ca)003:231: drug pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:232: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos /
NK005(ca)003:233: ji ltar yan lag bzhi pa las /
NK005(ca)003:235: rgyal ba sras bcas tshogs gyur pas //
NK005(ca)003:236: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu //
NK005(ca)003:237: thugs mchog rin chen bskyed pa ltar //
NK005(ca)003:238: bla med yang dag rdzogs pa yi //
NK005(ca)003:239: byang chub chen por sems bskyed de //
NK005(ca)003:240: rgyal ba rnams kyi rjes su slob //
NK005(ca)003:241: mdor na 'gro ba ma lus pa //
NK005(ca)003:242: sku gsum 'bras bu thob bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:243: dkyil 'khor drug gi sprul pa yis //
NK005(ca)003:244: rnam par rol pa'i don gnas bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:246: bdun pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:247: ye shes kyi 'khor lo mkha' khyab tu sad par byas la /
NK005(ca)003:248: h+aum a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:250: mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK005(ca)003:251: khyad par bstan pa'i mthu rtsal 'byung ba'i byin gyis
NK005(ca)003:252: brlab pa'i dbang mchog bskur ba'i dngos grub stsol ba'i
NK005(ca)003:254: byin chen byin phob dbang chen dbang bskur dngos grub mchog stsol bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:255: ces rol mo'i sgra dang spos chen gyis bdug cing /
NK005(ca)003:258: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs rnams bdag gnas yo byad thams cad la thim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)003:259: brgyad pa mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:260: rdzas thams cad la dmigs te /
NK005(ca)003:261: ma h+aa kro d+ha shwa r+ai sarba dra byam bi shwa d+ha ni h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK005(ca)003:262: rang gi thugs ka nas ram yam kham 'phros ye
NK005(ca)003:263: shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas mchod rdzas kyi
NK005(ca)003:264: dngos 'dzin nyes skyon thams cad bsregs gtor bkrus te
NK005(ca)003:265: stong par gyur / bye brag tu bdud rtsi /
NK005(ca)003:266: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sngon po zla gam ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:267: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum dmar po 'bar bas mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:268: de'i steng du kam las byung ba'i thod pa nang
NK005(ca)003:269: 'od gsal chags thogs med pa la gnas pa'i bdud
NK005(ca)003:270: rtsi lnga dang sgron ma lnga la h+aum h+r+aiht+r+aam h+aam
NK005(ca)003:271: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyi mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:272: de'i steng du a las zla ba la h+aum las byung ba'i rdo rje /
NK005(ca)003:273: rlung g.yos me sbar rdzas dang yi ge rnams zhu h+aum hi h+r+aihtram h+aam /
NK005(ca)003:274: zhes brjod pas rigs drug gi sa bon las phyag mtshan /
NK005(ca)003:275: de las skur gyur pa'i 'phro 'dus ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bkug nas rdo rje la zhugs /
NK005(ca)003:276: rdo rje dang zla ba snod du lhungs pa zhu ba las /
NK005(ca)003:277: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi kha dog dri ro nus
NK005(ca)003:278: mthu phun sum tshogs pa bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'od
NK005(ca)003:279: zer gyi phung por 'bar bar gyur /
NK005(ca)003:280: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aih zhes nyer gcig bzla /
NK005(ca)003:281: ma h+aa badz+ra tsakra man+da la h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:283: gtor rdzas h+aum hi h+r+aihh+aam las ye shes lnga'i rol
NK005(ca)003:284: pa 'dod yon gyi rnam pa cir yang 'char ba'i
NK005(ca)003:285: longs spyod kyi gter du gyur par bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)003:286: +aahh+aum te dz+wa ba lim ta ba la wa te gu h+ye sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:288: rigs rkyang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis dang rigs bsdus kyi skabs 'dir rak+ta yang bshams la /
NK005(ca)003:289: rak+ta'i snod a las b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i snod du rak+ta
NK005(ca)003:290: la ra yig dmar pos mtshan pa la khams gsum
NK005(ca)003:291: gyi rak+ta thams cad zhugs shing 'dres pa las dmar
NK005(ca)003:292: gyi rgya mtsho 'dod yon gyi rlabs phreng 'khrug par
NK005(ca)003:293: bsam zhing / ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK005(ca)003:295: rdzas thun mong ba rnams la /
NK005(ca)003:296: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum dang a las byung ba'i
NK005(ca)003:297: snod bzang por +aahh+aum las byung ba'i mchod pa'i rdzas
NK005(ca)003:298: rnams 'dod yon gyi khyad par mtha' yas par rang
NK005(ca)003:299: bzhin bde stong gi ye shes /
NK005(ca)003:300: rnam pa mchod rdzas kyi sprin phung /
NK005(ca)003:301: byed las dbang po drug zag med kyi bde bas
NK005(ca)003:302: tshim par nus pa nam mkha' gang ba rnams su
NK005(ca)003:306: badz+ra a ha ra h+r+aih na mahsarba ta th+aa ga
NK005(ca)003:307: te b+h+yo a lang+ka ra pa na bee h+aum s+w+aa
NK005(ca)003:308: h+aa / b+h+yo d+h+yam rat+na me g+ha s+pha ra na h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:309: zhes rol mo'i sgra sbyar ro //
NK005(ca)003:310: de dag ni sngon 'gro'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)003:314: dang po la rnal 'byor dngos dang /
NK005(ca)003:319: sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:321: 'di ltar dmigs pa'i yul bral sems kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)003:322: mtshan rtog kun las 'das pa ye shes che //
NK005(ca)003:323: ma bcos byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la //
NK005(ca)003:324: snang stong btang snyoms chen po'i ngang du gsal //
NK005(ca)003:325: d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)003:326: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs mtshan ma'i dmigs yul
NK005(ca)003:327: dang bral ba'i sems kyi dbyings stong nyid de bzhin
NK005(ca)003:329: 'gro la khyab pa'i thugs rje chen po ni //
NK005(ca)003:330: rtsol bral gsal ba'i ye shes lnga las byung //
NK005(ca)003:331: stong gsal byang chub sems kyis kun tu khyab //
NK005(ca)003:332: dmigs med snying rje chen po kun tu snang //
NK005(ca)003:333: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)003:334: ma rtogs pa'i 'gro la snying rje chen po rtsol
NK005(ca)003:335: bral ye shes kyi rang rtsal kun tu khyab par
NK005(ca)003:336: snang ba'o // 'phrul dag'i tshul byung rdo rje sems dpa' ni //
NK005(ca)003:337: stong gsum yang thog dag tu gnas mdzad de //
NK005(ca)003:338: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i skur shar ba //
NK005(ca)003:339: stong gsum gyi ni yang thog tu gnas pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:340: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga y+aa mi man+dala h+aum b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)003:342: skad cig tsam gyis e las nam mkha'i rang bzhin chos 'byung dkar po kun tu bzang mo'o //
NK005(ca)003:343: de'i nang du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sngon
NK005(ca)003:344: po gzhu'i dbyibs can rdo rje rgya gram dang ba
NK005(ca)003:345: dan gyis mtshan pa sgrol ma'o //
NK005(ca)003:346: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po bum pas mtshan pa m+aa ma k+ai'o //
NK005(ca)003:347: de'i steng du lam las dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)003:348: ser po gru bzhi rdo rjes mtshan pa spyan ma'o
NK005(ca)003:349: // der kham las byung ba'i 'o ma'i rgya mtsho'i
NK005(ca)003:350: dbus su sum las byung ba'i ri rab rin po
NK005(ca)003:351: che sna bzhi las grub pa rol mtsho ri dang
NK005(ca)003:352: // bcas pas brgyan / de'i steng du ram las
NK005(ca)003:353: ye shes gsal ba'i me 'od dkar po 'bar ba'i
NK005(ca)003:354: rtse mo gsum pa gos dkar mo'o //
NK005(ca)003:355: de dag ni gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK005(ca)003:357: de'i steng du pam las rin po che'i pad+ma la gser gyi 'khor lo /
NK005(ca)003:358: de'i lte bar h+aum las sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK005(ca)003:359: de'i dbus su b+h+r+aum las gzhal sa yas khang chen
NK005(ca)003:360: po gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs bzhis brgyan pa
NK005(ca)003:361: / nang nas rim pa bzhin du dkar mthing dmar
NK005(ca)003:362: ser ljang ba'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan
NK005(ca)003:363: pa las rang byung nyi shu rtsa lnga'i 'od zer
NK005(ca)003:364: / 'phro ba / pha gu dang d+r+wa ba d+r+wa
NK005(ca)003:365: phyed shar bu mda' yab 'dod pa'i snam bu sogs
NK005(ca)003:366: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs shing rgyan thams
NK005(ca)003:367: cad kyis rnam par brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)003:368: phyi'i khor yug la 'jig rten pa'i lha snam dkar po dang /
NK005(ca)003:369: pad+ma dang 'khor lo rdo rje'i ra ba me dpung 'bar bas bskor ba /
NK005(ca)003:370: phyi rol phyogs kyi mdog dang mtshungs pa'i gzhi la
NK005(ca)003:371: dur khrod chen po brgyad dur khrod kyi chas rnams
NK005(ca)003:373: de'i phyir dpag bsam gyi shing dang /
NK005(ca)003:377: rin po che'i phung po sogs 'dod yon sna tshogs kyis gang ba'i snam bu ser po /
NK005(ca)003:378: phyi nas rdo rje'i ra ba sngon pos bskor ba /
NK005(ca)003:379: gzhal yas khang chen po de'i nang gi steng 'og
NK005(ca)003:380: rnams shar dkar lho sngo nub dmar byang ser dbus
NK005(ca)003:381: ljang gu'o // nang gi phyogs bzhir ka ba gnyis gnyis kyis btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)003:382: gdung zlum gyis bres ba'i phyogs mtshams lte ba dang
NK005(ca)003:383: bcas pa'i re'u mig dgu la rigs drug gi dkyil
NK005(ca)003:385: gzhal med khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi sogs mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs pa dgu las /
NK005(ca)003:386: pho brang dbus ma rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)003:387: la dbus su zlum po rdo rje'i mu khyud can
NK005(ca)003:388: / shar du rnam snang gi dkyil 'khor zlum po 'khor lo'i mu khyud can /
NK005(ca)003:389: lhor he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor zla gam sgo gcig
NK005(ca)003:390: shar du blta ba thod pa'i rtsig pa dang khro
NK005(ca)003:391: bo'i rdo rje'i mu khyud can /
NK005(ca)003:392: nub tu gar dbang gi dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab ma
NK005(ca)003:393: brgyad pa'i dbyibs can ka ba dang mu khyud la
NK005(ca)003:395: byang du rdo rje nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rin po
NK005(ca)003:396: che zur brgyad pa'i dbyibs can rin po che'i mu
NK005(ca)003:397: khyud can / mtshams bzhir rta mchog rigs bzhi'i dkyil
NK005(ca)003:398: 'khor sna tshogs rdo rje'i mu khyud can phrin las
NK005(ca)003:399: bzhi'i khyad par las shar dang shar lho /
NK005(ca)003:402: byang dang byang shar rnams mtshungs pa ste /
NK005(ca)003:403: thams cad kyang ling tshe dgu dgu dang ldan pa las /
NK005(ca)003:404: lho dang lho nub kyi ling tshe dgu la zla
NK005(ca)003:405: gam nang bstan dgu dang zhing gi 'phan gdugs sogs
NK005(ca)003:407: lho ma'i dbus su pad+ma dregs byed nyi zla brtsegs pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:408: re mig brgyad la bam chen re'i gdan gyis khyad par du byas pa /
NK005(ca)003:409: dkyil 'khor gzhan rnams kyi dbus kyi ling tshe la pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i gdan re re /
NK005(ca)003:410: mtshams kyi 'dab ma rnams la rin po che'i bum
NK005(ca)003:411: pa bdud rtsis gang ba thod pas kha brgyan pa
NK005(ca)003:412: re re / phyogs mtshams kyi re'u mig brgyad dang
NK005(ca)003:413: dkyil 'khor thams cad la mtshungs par sgo bzhi dang
NK005(ca)003:414: grwa bzhir pad+ma'i gdan re re'o //
NK005(ca)003:415: de dag ni rten gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK005(ca)003:416: gsum pa sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhi ste /
NK005(ca)003:420: rnal 'byor chen po dang bzhi las /
NK005(ca)003:422: dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i gtso bo'i gnas su pad+ma dang
NK005(ca)003:423: nyi zla'i gdan la rang gi sems nyid dpal mchog
NK005(ca)003:424: dang por bzhugs par mdzad de /
NK005(ca)003:425: yod pa ma yin med pa min //
NK005(ca)003:426: dbu mar yang ni dmigs su med //
NK005(ca)003:427: shes rab pha rol phyin sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)003:428: sangs rgyas byang chub rab bsgrub pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:429: zhes chos thams cad stong pa nyid dang mtshan ma
NK005(ca)003:430: med pa dang smon pa med pa dang rang bzhin
NK005(ca)003:431: gyis 'od gsal ba'i ting 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK005(ca)003:432: pa la / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams kyis 'gro ba'i don la bskul ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:434: rgyud kyis semasacana ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas pa /
NK005(ca)003:435: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab tu sprul /
NK005(ca)003:437: rnam pa mang po rab tu dga' ba'i rgyud kyis
NK005(ca)003:438: sems can ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas
NK005(ca)003:439: pa // de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma
NK005(ca)003:440: bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab tu sprul rol
NK005(ca)003:441: pa // rnam par sprul // h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:442: rnam pa mang po khro bo'i rgyud kyis sems can ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)003:443: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab tu rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)003:444: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:445: rnam pa mang po srog gi rgyud kyis sems can ma lus lus pa med par 'dul mkhas pa //
NK005(ca)003:446: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi sgyu ma bde mchog sgyu mas thams cad rab tu rnam par sprul //
NK005(ca)003:457: am ah zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dbyangs kyis mtshan pa me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK005(ca)003:458: de'i steng du ka kha ga g+ha nga /
NK005(ca)003:466: nga ro dang rnam bcad rnams las byung ba'i nyi
NK005(ca)003:467: ma'i dbyangs gsal gnyis kyang byang sems gnyis tshogs gnyis
NK005(ca)003:468: mtshan dpe gnyis kyi ngo bo /
NK005(ca)003:470: dkyil 'khor gsal byed kyis mtshan pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK005(ca)003:471: nyi zla'i 'od kyis 'phro 'dus h+aum du gyur /
NK005(ca)003:472: de las rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa 'od
NK005(ca)003:473: zer dmar po 'phro ba'i lte bar h+aum gis mtshan
NK005(ca)003:474: pa ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK005(ca)003:475: de las 'od 'phros rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor sprul /
NK005(ca)003:476: sems can thams cad rdo rje gsum gyi go 'phang la bkod /
NK005(ca)003:477: slar 'dus te thim pas 'od zer rab tu 'bar
NK005(ca)003:478: bar gyur pa ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes
NK005(ca)003:481: de thams cad yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:482: sems dpa'i sku yongs su rdzogs pa ni chos kyi
NK005(ca)003:484: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aah dzahh+aum bam hoh su ra ti s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:485: zhes nga rgyal bzung nas gsal gdab pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:486: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK005(ca)003:487: bde ba chen po kun tu bzang po rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:488: 'chang dung dang kun+da zla ba'i 'od ltar dkar ba
NK005(ca)003:489: la cung zad dmar ba'i mdangs can /
NK005(ca)003:490: 'jo sgeg dgyes pa'i 'dzum mig g.yo zhing chags pa'i nyams rgyas pa /
NK005(ca)003:493: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar rgyab ser ba /
NK005(ca)003:494: phyag g.yas kyi dang pos 'bar ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa gsor zhing /
NK005(ca)003:495: g.yon gyi dang po dril bu dpyangs pa'i kha t+w+aam ka 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK005(ca)003:496: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:497: mtshan dang dpe byad kyis mdzes pa /
NK005(ca)003:498: dar dkar po gser gyi ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK005(ca)003:499: sku smad tshi gu'i na bza' can /
NK005(ca)003:500: rin po che'i dbu rgyan sked chings mgur chun sogs rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)003:501: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs shing /
NK005(ca)003:502: rang 'dra ba'i kun tu bzang mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK005(ca)003:503: de nas rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtugs te /
NK005(ca)003:504: namahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK005(ca)003:505: gu na karma badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK005(ca)003:506: / lus kyi ba spu'i gnas thams cad du rigs
NK005(ca)003:507: drug gi lha'i rdul phra rab kyis khyab par bsam
NK005(ca)003:508: / la / rdo rjee thal mo las mthe bong
NK005(ca)003:509: bsnol gung mdzub rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i tshul du
NK005(ca)003:510: byas pa nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma'i rgyas spyi mgrin
NK005(ca)003:511: snying lte sogs gnas thams cad du reg ste /
NK005(ca)003:512: d+harma d+ha tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)003:516: thugs kar nyi ma la rang 'dra'i ye shes sems
NK005(ca)003:517: dpa'i thugs kar ting 'dzin sems dpa' h+aum dkar po
NK005(ca)003:518: / de las 'od zer 'phros ye shes pa pheem zhes spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)003:519: thugs ka nas sprul pa'i lha mo rnams kyis bdud rtsi'i bum pas khrus gsol zhing dbang bskur /
NK005(ca)003:520: dzahh+aum bam hoh spyi bo nas zhugs te dam tshig
NK005(ca)003:521: pa dang dbyer med du gyur pa la dbang rtags
NK005(ca)003:522: su de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan par
NK005(ca)003:523: bsam la nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma'i phyag rgya mgo
NK005(ca)003:527: sor mo thams cad nang du bsnol //
NK005(ca)003:528: rtse mo'i ngos rnams kun sprad la //
NK005(ca)003:529: mthe bos rdo rje mnan pa ni //
NK005(ca)003:530: sna dang mig phug lta bu ste //
NK005(ca)003:531: zhes pa'i thod skam gyi phyag rgya yang gnas lngar gtugs la /
NK005(ca)003:533: rin po che'i phyag rgya spyi bor btugs la /
NK005(ca)003:534: rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK005(ca)003:535: rdo rje khu tshur dpral mgrin sogs gnas lngar reg la /
NK005(ca)003:537: phata lam ba a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:538: badz+ra tush+ya hoh zhes dar dpyangs 'ching 'grol gyi phyag rgya yang bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:539: de dag ni dang po'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK005(ca)003:541: rjes su chags pa'i rnam mang bde ba'i pad+mo rnams //
NK005(ca)003:542: dga' ba'i mchod pas gsal bar rjes su mchod byas pas //
NK005(ca)003:543: mchog tu rtag pa'i rnal 'byor bde bas bde grub mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:545: mchog tu bde ba'i dam tshig ngo bo nyid //
NK005(ca)003:546: mchog tu bde ba'i rnal 'byor skal bzang mchog dgyes pa //
NK005(ca)003:547: rang gi dam tshig rtag par rol cig pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:548: zhes glu blangs nas yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las
NK005(ca)003:549: rdo rje 'bar ba nor bu'i rtse mo can phata
NK005(ca)003:550: kyis mtshan pa / yum gyi gsang gnas +aahls pad+ma
NK005(ca)003:551: ser po 'dab ma brgyad pa phyi rol chos 'byung
NK005(ca)003:552: gi dbyibs can ze 'bru +aahs mtshan pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:553: de nas stong pa shin tu zhes sogs kyi glu len pa'am /
NK005(ca)003:555: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:556: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)003:557: a la la hoh zhes snyoms par zhugs pas bde
NK005(ca)003:558: ba chen po'i 'od zer gyis sangs rgyas thams cad
NK005(ca)003:559: mnyes shing bskul / sems can thams cad kyi dri ma sbyangs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)003:560: de ni rjes su rnal 'byor ro //
NK005(ca)003:562: de nas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad rigs drug
NK005(ca)003:563: gi gsung yi ger gyur pa rnams rang gi ba
NK005(ca)003:565: bde ba chen po'i gnas su 'dus te byang chub
NK005(ca)003:566: kyi sems dang ro gcig tu gyur pa 'khor lo
NK005(ca)003:567: bzhi nas brgyad brtag ste nor bu'i rtse mor phyin
NK005(ca)003:568: / yang rjes su chags pa'i 'od zer gyis 'gro ba thams cad sbyangs /
NK005(ca)003:569: rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor dang rdo rje rnam pa gsum gyi go 'phang la bkod /
NK005(ca)003:570: slar 'dus te thim pa yum gyi gsang gnas su
NK005(ca)003:571: gzhal yas khang so so'i gdan dang bcas pa'i lha
NK005(ca)003:572: gnas rnams su rang mdog dang mthun pa'i thig le
NK005(ca)003:573: re re / de rnams yongs su gyur pa las
NK005(ca)003:574: chos kyi snying po'i yi ge rnams su gyur pa
NK005(ca)003:575: re re / ni / dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i lte
NK005(ca)003:576: ba la h+aum las bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:577: sems dpa' la sogs te rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)003:578: dgu'i lha tshogs rnams su gyur /
NK005(ca)003:579: de dag gtso 'khor rim pa bzhin mkha' nang nas phyir spros /
NK005(ca)003:580: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aah dzahh+aum bam hoh su ra tas+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:581: rang nyid lta bu'i sprul pa dpag tu med pa
NK005(ca)003:582: spros chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba la sogs pa
NK005(ca)003:583: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa khyad par can thams cad
NK005(ca)003:584: mdzad / sems can thams cad rgyal ba rigs drug
NK005(ca)003:585: gi go 'phang la bkod nas rim pa bzhin 'dus
NK005(ca)003:586: mdzad / pa las / gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' rang nyid la thim par gyur /
NK005(ca)003:587: de bzhin du 'khor gyi lha mo rnams kyang rgyas par rang sngags kyis 'byin pa yin yang /
NK005(ca)003:588: bsdu na sa bon gyis phyungs pas kyang chog pas /
NK005(ca)003:590: dzahbade mchog ma dkar mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK005(ca)003:591: h+aum e ma bde ba ma gser mdog ling+ga rdo
NK005(ca)003:592: rjes mtshan pa dang b+ha ga rin po ches mtshan
NK005(ca)003:593: pa / bam snang mdzad ma dmar mo sna tshogs
NK005(ca)003:594: rdo rje dang bdud rtsi'i thod pa 'dzin cing kha
NK005(ca)003:596: hohsloba pa mo ljang gu g.yas 'khyud pa'i tshul gyis
NK005(ca)003:597: mda' dang g.yon sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs kyis mtshan
NK005(ca)003:598: pa'i bdud rtsi'i bum pa 'dzin pa rnams dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)003:599: dbus ma'i pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi la shar sogs g.yas
NK005(ca)003:601: sangs rgyas byang chub ma dkar dmar tshangs pa'i mgo
NK005(ca)003:602: bos mtshan pa'i mda' bzhi dus gcig tu 'phen pa'i
NK005(ca)003:605: chos kyi 'khor lo ma dkar ser g.yas pa'i gung
NK005(ca)003:606: mo la 'khor lo dmar po dang sngon po gnyis
NK005(ca)003:607: bskor zhing g.yon dkur brten pa /
NK005(ca)003:608: hah khams gsum rnam rgyal ma dmar skya g.yas mdung
NK005(ca)003:609: rtse gsum dang g.yon rdo rje thugs kar brten pa
NK005(ca)003:611: 'dod pa'i dbang mo ljang gu dpag bsam shing gi
NK005(ca)003:612: lcug ma rlung gis bskyod pa 'dzin cing gar mdzad
NK005(ca)003:613: pa rnams re mig brgyad kyi shar sogs phyogs bzhir
NK005(ca)003:615: gling bu ma sngon mo gling bu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:618: pi wang ma ser mo pi wang /
NK005(ca)003:620: rnga chen ma dmar mo rnga chen /
NK005(ca)003:622: rdza rnga ma ljang gu rdza rnga 'dzin pa rnams
NK005(ca)003:623: re mig gi mtshams bzhir shar lho nas g.yas bskor
NK005(ca)003:625: me tog ma dmar ser me tog /
NK005(ca)003:626: +aah spos me ma dkar mo spos me /
NK005(ca)003:627: +aamh mar me ma dmar mo mar me /
NK005(ca)003:628: +aah dri chab ma ljang gu dri chab 'dzin pa
NK005(ca)003:629: rnams phyi'i grwa bzhi la me nas brtsams te g.yas
NK005(ca)003:630: bskor gyis 'khod / brgyad ka'i phyag mtshan rdo rje mtshan cing /
NK005(ca)003:631: lha mo bcu drug po rnams sgeg mdzes chags pa'i
NK005(ca)003:632: nyams can dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad
NK005(ca)003:633: kyis brgyan cing / 'od kyi dkyil 'khor 'bar ba
NK005(ca)003:634: 'gying bag gi tshul dang sems dpa'i skyil mo krung
NK005(ca)003:635: kyis brgyan cing / gis bzhugs pa'o // de dag
NK005(ca)003:636: ni rdor sems kyi khyad par gyi lha tshogs so
NK005(ca)003:637: kyis brgyan cing / gis bzhugs pa'o // // dzah
NK005(ca)003:638: rta mgrin 'phangs mtho ma dkar mo rta gdong can
NK005(ca)003:639: lcags kyu dang thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin
NK005(ca)003:640: kyis brgyan cing / gis bzhugs pa'o // // pa / h+aum&a /
NK005(ca)003:641: phag gdong ma sngon mo mche ba dang zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:643: snang ba ma dmar mo khyi gdong nyi zlas mtshan pa'i lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:644: hoh thal ba 'jigs byed ma ljang gu seng ge'i
NK005(ca)003:645: gdong can dril bu dang 'od dpag med kyi skus
NK005(ca)003:646: mtshan pa'i thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin pa
NK005(ca)003:647: rnams zung re spros te dkyil 'khor dbus ma dang
NK005(ca)003:648: gzhi dkyil gyi shar sogs sgo bzhi la g.yos bskor
NK005(ca)003:649: gyis 'khod / de thams cad kyang phyag mtshan rdo
NK005(ca)003:650: rjes mtshan pa gtum zhing khros pa dur khrod kyi
NK005(ca)003:651: chas can 'bar ba me'i dbus na g.yon brkyang gis
NK005(ca)003:652: gyis 'khod / gnas pa'o // gzhan du g.yas brkyang du bshad kyang rung /
NK005(ca)003:654: de dag ni rdor sems dang gzhi dkyil gyi sgo ba rnams so //
NK005(ca)003:656: zhes phyungs pas spro ba dang bsdu ba'i phrin las
NK005(ca)003:657: mdzad de dkyil 'khor shar ma'i dbus su 'khod pa
NK005(ca)003:658: ni / rgyal ba rtag pa rnam par snang mdzad
NK005(ca)003:659: dkar la ser ba'i mdangs can rtsa zhal dkar po
NK005(ca)003:660: g.yas ser g.yon dmar rgyab ljang ba /
NK005(ca)003:661: phyag dang po gnyis kyi stod g.yogs chos gos ngur
NK005(ca)003:662: smrig gsol ba'i gra dang lhung bzed bdud rtsis gang
NK005(ca)003:663: ba / 'og ma gnyis kyis mkhar gsil dang glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:664: 'khor los sgyur ba'i cha lugs dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)003:665: sangs rgyas spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo dang thod pa 'dzin pas 'khyud pa /
NK005(ca)003:666: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:669: sangs rgyas kun brjod ma dkar mo ljags kyis mtshan pa'i pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:671: shin tu rgyal ba ma ser mo phyag gnyis thal mo rdeb pa /
NK005(ca)003:673: kun nas bzang mo dmar mo rdo rje rtse lnga dang rin po che'i za ma tog 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:675: mi zad pa'i snod ma sna tshogs mdog nor bus
NK005(ca)003:676: gang ba'i snod dang chos dung 'dzin pa rnams pad+ma'i
NK005(ca)003:677: 'dab ma bzhi la shar sogs g.yas bskor gyis 'khod
NK005(ca)003:679: sangs rgyas kun ldan ma dmar ser rgyal ba mi bskyod pa'i sku thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:681: zhal bzang ma dkar mo me long gi mdog can me long dang rnga yab 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:683: sprin chen ma sngon mo ser ba 'bebs pa'i rdo rje'i sprin 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:685: nam mkha'i spyan ma ser skya pad+ma mig 'bras kyis
NK005(ca)003:686: mtshan pa 'dzin pa rnams re mig brgyad kyi shar
NK005(ca)003:687: sogs phyogs bzhir g.yas bskor gyis 'khod //
NK005(ca)003:688: gling bu ma zhes pa nas 'bar ba'i me'i dbus
NK005(ca)003:689: na g.yon brkyang gis gnas pa'o'i bar gyi mchod lha
NK005(ca)003:690: brgyad dang sgo ma bzhi po sngar dang 'dra ba
NK005(ca)003:691: las / khyad par bdud rtsis gang ba 'dzin pa
NK005(ca)003:692: rnams spros te sgo bzhi la g.yas bskor gyis 'khod
NK005(ca)003:694: phyag mtshan rdo rjes mtshan pa zhes pa'i gnas su
NK005(ca)003:695: 'khor los mtshan pa zhes bsgyur te rnam snang gi
NK005(ca)003:696: lha tshogs so // he ru badz+ra sa ma ya
NK005(ca)003:697: h+r+aihsarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu dra pra b+hany+dza ka
NK005(ca)003:698: lha tshogs so // h+aum phata / ces dang /
NK005(ca)003:699: h+aum zhes phyungs pas spro bsdu'i phrin las mdzad de dkyil 'khor lho ma'i dbus su 'khod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:700: dpal chen he ru ka sku mdog sngon po rab
NK005(ca)003:701: tu khros pa'i rtsa zhal mthing nag 'bar ba chen
NK005(ca)003:703: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar rgyab ser ba ste zhal bzhi pa /
NK005(ca)003:704: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK005(ca)003:707: spyan dmar ldog cing dbu skra dang sma ra 'bar ba /
NK005(ca)003:710: phyag brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu dpyangs pa'i kha t+w+aam ka /
NK005(ca)003:711: gnyis pa gnyis kyis 'jigs byed chen po'i pags pa rlung gis bskyod pa'i tshul can /
NK005(ca)003:712: gsum pa gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu /
NK005(ca)003:713: bzhi pa gnyis kyis thod pa khrag gis gang ba dang /
NK005(ca)003:714: snying chen pos gang ba 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:715: dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK005(ca)003:716: zhabs g.yas cung zad bskum pas yum gyi barla la
NK005(ca)003:717: 'khyud cing g.yon brkyang ba'i skyil krung phyed pa'i gar
NK005(ca)003:718: stabs kyis gu lang dang dbang chen dang zla ba
NK005(ca)003:719: dang nyi ma dang gshin rje dang tshangs pa la
NK005(ca)003:720: sogs pa dregs pa can thams cad gnon pa /
NK005(ca)003:721: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma sngo skya thod khrag
NK005(ca)003:722: dang ba dan rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya can gyis
NK005(ca)003:724: he ru ka phyag bzhi pa /
NK005(ca)003:725: g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK005(ca)003:726: g.yon gnyis gshol thong dang zhags pa /
NK005(ca)003:727: lha chen gyi g.yang gzhi stod g.yogs su mnab pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:729: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK005(ca)003:730: kha t+w+aam ka se ral khar byas pa /
NK005(ca)003:731: yum yang kha t+w+aam ka rgyab phyogs su se ral khal brten par byas kyang rung ngo //
NK005(ca)003:732: gang ltar yang sngar bzhin du /
NK005(ca)003:733: h+r+aih goo r+ai dkar ser zhi ba'i mdangs can zhal bzhi pa /
NK005(ca)003:734: phyag brgyad kyis mda' gzhu 'gengs pas tshangs pa'i mgo bzhi 'bigs pa /
NK005(ca)003:736: tsoo r+ai dmar ser drag mo'i nyams can g.yas gung
NK005(ca)003:737: mos 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa gtod cing g.yon thugs
NK005(ca)003:738: kar lcags kyu 'dzin pas kha t+w+aam ka la 'khyud
NK005(ca)003:740: phra mo dmar nag rmongs byed kyi tshul can steng zhal phag gi gdong can /
NK005(ca)003:741: phyag dang po gnyis rtse gsum dang thod pa /
NK005(ca)003:742: 'og ma gnyis 'khor lo dang khu tshur bcangs pa g.yas brkyang ba'i stabs can /
NK005(ca)003:744: bee ta l+ai dkar mo shi ba slong ba'i tshul can /
NK005(ca)003:745: thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba dang ba dan gsum
NK005(ca)003:746: pa'i phyag rgya mdzad pa rnams phyogs kyi re mig
NK005(ca)003:748: puk+ka s+ai sna tshogs mdog gar gyi stangs can /
NK005(ca)003:749: rdo rje rtse lnga dang dpag bsam shing gi lcug ma 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:750: sku mdog gi khyad par ni /
NK005(ca)003:751: bol bzhi barla dpung dkar ba la //
NK005(ca)003:752: lus sgrom nywa bzhi dmar ba ste //
NK005(ca)003:753: phyag mchog lo ma sngon po 'dra //
NK005(ca)003:754: zhes gsungs shing zhal ras sngon po don gyis thob pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:756: tsan+da l+ai sngo nag dbugs bskyod pa'i tshul can g.yas
NK005(ca)003:757: rlung ras rdo rjes mtshan pa dang g.yon tri sh+aul
NK005(ca)003:759: g+hasma r+ai ser nag mi ro za ba'i tshul can ral gri dang me thab 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:761: sme sha ma mthing nag rnam par g.yeng ba'i tshul can g.yas gnyis rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK005(ca)003:762: g.yon gnyis gshor thong dang zhags pa kha t+w+aam ka
NK005(ca)003:763: se ral khar thogs pa rnams mtshams kyi re mig
NK005(ca)003:764: bzhi la 'khod / khro mo brgyad po zhing lpags
NK005(ca)003:765: dang dar gyi na bza' gsol zhing sbrul dang thod
NK005(ca)003:766: phreng rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)003:767: pad nyi ro'i gdan la gar stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:769: mda' 'dzin ma dkar mo mda' gzhu thogs pa /
NK005(ca)003:771: kha t+w+aam 'dzin ma ser mo kha t+w+aam dril bur bcas pa thogs pa /
NK005(ca)003:773: 'khor lo 'dzin ma dmar ser 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:775: sna tshogs ba dan 'dzin ma ljang gu ba dan
NK005(ca)003:776: la dril bu dpyangs pa 'dzin pa rnams gru chad
NK005(ca)003:777: kyi grwa bzhi la me nas brtsams te g.yas bskor
NK005(ca)003:778: gyis 'khod / me tog ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)003:779: sgo ma bzhi ni sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK005(ca)003:780: sgeg mdzes chags pa'i gnas su khro bo'i nyams dang ldan cing zhes dang /
NK005(ca)003:781: phyag mtshan gyi skabs khro bo'i rdo rjes mtshan pa zhes bsgyur /
NK005(ca)003:782: de dag ni he ru ka'i lha tshogs so //
NK005(ca)003:783: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa nit+te shwa r+aa h+r+aihdzah zhes dang /
NK005(ca)003:784: h+r+aih zhes phyungs pas spro bsdu'i phrin las mdzad de /
NK005(ca)003:785: dkyil dkyil 'khor nub ma'i dbus su 'khod pa ni
NK005(ca)003:786: pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug dmar la dkar ba'i mdangs
NK005(ca)003:787: can mtshan dpe'i lang tshos sgeg cing chags pa'i nyams
NK005(ca)003:788: dang ldan pa / phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis chos 'chad kyis pad+ma'i sdong bu gnyis 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:789: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'dzin cing dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK005(ca)003:790: yum gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma dang thod khrag 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK005(ca)003:791: zhabs g.yas brkyang pa'i rgyal po rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:793: zhal bco lnga nyams dang kha dog sna tshogs pa /
NK005(ca)003:794: rtsa zhal sku lus dang mtshungs pa'i mdog can /
NK005(ca)003:795: phyag g.yas lnga bcus rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen
NK005(ca)003:796: dbyug pa ral gri sogs mtshon cha sna tshogs pa
NK005(ca)003:797: dang / g.yon lnga bcus kha dog sna tshogs pa'i pad+ma'i sdong bu 'ba' zhig 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:798: zhabs nyi shu rtsa bzhi g.yas brkyang pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK005(ca)003:800: de ltar byas na'ang legs so //
NK005(ca)003:801: gang ltar yang 'khor rnams sngar bzhin du /
NK005(ca)003:802: dzah rnam gzigs ma dmar mo phyag g.yon pas pad+ma
NK005(ca)003:803: dmar po snyems pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin cing g.yas pas
NK005(ca)003:805: sgrol ma ljang gu g.yon pad+ma sngon po'i sdong bu dkur brten cing g.yas pas de nyid 'dren pa /
NK005(ca)003:807: sa 'dzin ma sngon mo g.yas 'khor lo dang g.yon pad dkar 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:808: hoh khro gnyer ma dkar mo g.yas mdung rtse gsum
NK005(ca)003:809: pa'i phyag rgyas gar byed cing g.yon ut+pala sngon po
NK005(ca)003:810: 'dzin pa rnams pad+ma'i 'dab ma bzhi la shar sogs
NK005(ca)003:813: gtum pa'i dbang phyug ma dkar mo g.yas rdo rje gtod cing g.yon pad+ma dmar po 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:815: sna tshogs pad+mo ma sngo ljang g.yas 'khor lo gyen du gtod cing g.yon sna tshogs pad+mo 'jin pa /
NK005(ca)003:816: +aah pad+ma'i na bza' ma gser mdog can /
NK005(ca)003:817: g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan dang g.yon pad+ma ser po 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:818: hoh pad+ma'i dbang phyug ma dmar mo g.yas rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:819: rtse lnga gsor zhing g.yon pad+ma dmar po 'dzin pa
NK005(ca)003:820: rnams re mig brgyad kyi shar sogs 'gre /
NK005(ca)003:821: gling bu ma sogs sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK005(ca)003:822: phyag mtshan gyi skabs pad+mas mtshan pa /
NK005(ca)003:823: chags pa'i nyams can pad+ma'i phreng bas klubs pa dar dang rin po che zhes bsgyur /
NK005(ca)003:824: de dag ni gar dbang gi lha tshogs so //
NK005(ca)003:827: sid+d+h+ya ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na ba ba ta ta tram /
NK005(ca)003:830: zhes phyungs pas spro bsdu'i phrin las mdzad de dkyil 'khor byang ma'i dbus su 'khod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:831: rdo rje nyi ma sku mdog gser gyi mdog can
NK005(ca)003:832: zhal bzhi ser ba res 'ga' dmar zhing yid tsam
NK005(ca)003:833: khro ba / phal cher lhag par 'dzum pas bzhad pa /
NK005(ca)003:834: phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu /
NK005(ca)003:835: 'og ma gnyis kyis ral gri 'phyar zhing nyi ma'i
NK005(ca)003:836: dkyil 'khor dang rdo rjes mtshan pa'i pad+ma bsnams pa
NK005(ca)003:837: rin po che sna bdun gyis brgyan cing /
NK005(ca)003:838: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK005(ca)003:839: yum m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo rin po che dang thod pa 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK005(ca)003:841: dbang bskur ma dmar mo rdo rjes mtshan pa'i rin po che'i cod pan 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:842: h+r+aih gter ldan ma ser mo rin po ches gang ba'i bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:843: hoh rgyal mtshan mchog ldan ma dkar dmar rgyal mtshan nor bu'i tog can 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:845: mchod chen ma ljang gu zas sna tshogs kyis gang
NK005(ca)003:846: ba'i snod 'dzin pa rnams pad+ma'i 'dab ma bzhi la
NK005(ca)003:848: dzah mda' gzhu ma dmar ser mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:850: ral gri ma sgon mo ral gri kha t+w+aam 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:852: nyi ma ma dmar ser nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:853: hoh me 'bar ma ljang dmar rdo rjes mtshan pa'i
NK005(ca)003:854: me thab 'dzin pa rnams re mig brgyad kyi shar
NK005(ca)003:855: sogs 'gre / gling bu ma sogs sngar dang 'dra ba las /
NK005(ca)003:856: phyag mtshan gyi skabs nor bu rin po ches mtshan pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:857: lha mo bcu drug po rnams sku la nor bu
NK005(ca)003:858: dmar po'i mdangs 'od 'phro zhing sgeg mdzes zhes bsgyur
NK005(ca)003:859: / de dag ni rdo rje'i nyi ma'i lha tshogs so //
NK005(ca)003:863: zhes phyungs pas spro bsdu'i phrin las mdzad de mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi'i dbus su 'khod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:864: rta mchog rol pa'i sangs rgyas sku lus ljang gu /
NK005(ca)003:866: g.yas sngo g.yon dkar steng zhal rta gdong ljang gu mgrin pa gtod de sgra 'byin pa /
NK005(ca)003:867: phyag brgyad kyi g.yas bzhis ba dan rtse gsum pa'i
NK005(ca)003:868: phyag rgya dang rgya gram dang ral gri dang mda'
NK005(ca)003:869: 'dzin pa / g.yon bzhi'i sna tshogs pad+ma dang shak+ti dang be con dang gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK005(ca)003:870: zhabs bzhi g.yas brkyang ba'i dang pos sum grub ma dang dpal mo /
NK005(ca)003:871: gnyis pas zhi ba ma dang dga' ba ma /
NK005(ca)003:872: g.yon bskum pa'i dang pos drag po dang khyab 'jug /
NK005(ca)003:873: gnyis pas 'dod lha dang tshangs pa mnan pa /
NK005(ca)003:874: zhabs mthing nas rdo rje'i rmig pa 'byin pas de dag 'ching bar mdzad pa /
NK005(ca)003:875: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs spyan gsum pa /
NK005(ca)003:876: skra dmar ser gyen du bardzesa shing khro bo dang
NK005(ca)003:877: sgeg pa dang drag po dang zhi ba la sogs
NK005(ca)003:878: pa gar gyi nyams dgu dang ldan pa /
NK005(ca)003:879: gru mo phan chad kyi phyag rnams dmar zhing pus mo man chad kyi zhabs rnams nag po /
NK005(ca)003:880: rang 'od kyi yum dam tshig sgrol ma ljang skya
NK005(ca)003:881: sna tshogs rdo rje dang thod pa 'dzin pas nges
NK005(ca)003:883: dz+aih rta mchog gi g.yas su lha mo sna tshogs pad+ma ma ljang ser /
NK005(ca)003:884: hah g.yon du lha mo sna tshogs rdo rje ma ljang gu /
NK005(ca)003:885: gnyis ka'ang g.yas rang ming dang mthun pa'i phyag mtshan dang /
NK005(ca)003:886: g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa khro mo'i cha byad rdzogs pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:887: de ltar lha mo gnyis kyis lhag pa las /
NK005(ca)003:888: 'khor gzhan ni phrin las kyi bye brag las shar
NK005(ca)003:889: lho shar dang mtshungs pa sogs phyogs mtshams zung re
NK005(ca)003:890: mthun zhing / khyad par sku dang phyag mtshan la
NK005(ca)003:891: sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan cing don yod grub pas
NK005(ca)003:892: mthun zhing / dbu brgyan pa'o // de yang rdor
NK005(ca)003:893: sems dang rnam snang gi lha rnams sems dpa'i skyil
NK005(ca)003:894: mthun zhing / dbu brgyan pa'o // krung / he
NK005(ca)003:895: ru ka'i lha rnams skyil krung phyed pa'i gar stabs
NK005(ca)003:896: mthun zhing / dbu brgyan pa'o // krung / /
NK005(ca)003:897: gar dbang gi lha rnams skyil krung phyed pa'i rol
NK005(ca)003:898: mthun zhing / dbu brgyan pa'o // krung / /
NK005(ca)003:899: stabs / nyi ma'i lha rnams rdo rje'i skyil krung
NK005(ca)003:900: mthun zhing / dbu brgyan pa'o // krung / /
NK005(ca)003:901: stabs / / rta mchog gi lha rnams khro bo'i
NK005(ca)003:903: de ltar ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams mngon du
NK005(ca)003:904: bzhengs pa na nyi ma dang 'od zer gyi tshul
NK005(ca)003:905: du / shar du lha chen brgyad dang phyogs skyong /
NK005(ca)003:906: lhor gshin rje dang ma mo'i tshogs /
NK005(ca)003:907: nub tu pho nya dang klu chen brgyad /
NK005(ca)003:908: byang du gnod sbyin brgyad dang 'byung po'i tshogs /
NK005(ca)003:909: gzhan yang bka' sdod dam can srid pa gsum gyi
NK005(ca)003:910: 'byung po dkyil 'khor la mngon par dad pa mtha'
NK005(ca)003:911: yas pa'i tshogs rnams kyi phyi rol 'jig rten pa'i
NK005(ca)003:913: de dag ni shin tu rnal 'byor zhes bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:915: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad kyi mig dang gzugs phung la rnam par snang mdzad /
NK005(ca)003:916: rna ba dang tshor ba la rdo rje nyi ma /
NK005(ca)003:917: lce dang 'du shes la pad+ma gar dbang /
NK005(ca)003:918: sna dang 'du byed la rta mchog /
NK005(ca)003:919: yid dang rnam shes la he ru ka /
NK005(ca)003:920: lus dang ye shes la rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK005(ca)003:921: snying ga'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas ye
NK005(ca)003:922: shes kyi 'khor lo badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo
NK005(ca)003:923: rje bsdu ba'i rgya dang bcas pas spyan drangs par
NK005(ca)003:924: bsam la / dmigs med yan lag bzhi pa las 'di ltar ro //
NK005(ca)003:925: mkha' ltar dag pa khyab pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:926: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK005(ca)003:927: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)003:928: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:929: bsnyengs pa mi mnga' stobs bcu'i shugs ldan cing //
NK005(ca)003:930: ma 'dres sangs rgyas chos rnams rab tu rdzogs //
NK005(ca)003:931: dpa' bo chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:932: mkha' 'gro kun dang thabs gcig gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:933: thugs rje chen po'i sku mnga' gsung nyid rdzogs //
NK005(ca)003:934: mi 'jigs thugs mnga' seng+gesa bskyod du med //
NK005(ca)003:935: gdug pa'i tshogs mang zil gyis gnon mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)003:936: bcom ldan 'gro la brtse slad gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:938: stong pa shin tu zhes pa'i sh+lo ka gcig po bzhag /
NK005(ca)003:940: stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthus //
NK005(ca)003:941: nam mkha' nyid du dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK005(ca)003:942: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:943: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK005(ca)003:944: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma
NK005(ca)003:945: h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma
NK005(ca)003:946: ya s+t+wam / zhes mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la badz+ra push+pe pu /
NK005(ca)003:949: sarba p+au dza s+pha ra na h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:951: thugs ka nas sprul pa'i lha mo bzhis bdud rtsi'i
NK005(ca)003:952: bum pas khrus byas shing gnas gsum du dbang bskur
NK005(ca)003:953: / dri ma thams cad dang bral bar byas /
NK005(ca)003:954: lha rnams kyi spyi bo nas gnyis su med par thim par bsam la /
NK005(ca)003:956: bde gshegs pho brang dam pa 'dir //
NK005(ca)003:957: 'gro ba ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:958: don gyi dbang gis dgongs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:959: 'khor bcas gshegs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:960: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)003:961: zhes dam tshig pa la dbyer med du bzhugs par gsol /
NK005(ca)003:962: de nas phyag rgyas dbang bskur ba'i phyir /
NK005(ca)003:963: nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma'i rgya mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag ste /
NK005(ca)003:966: rat+na a b+hi a shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK005(ca)003:967: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah
NK005(ca)003:968: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu rgyan par
NK005(ca)003:969: bsam la / rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa tram /
NK005(ca)003:971: zhes rin po che'i phreng ba dang dar dpyangs 'ching 'grol bya /
NK005(ca)003:972: trum badz+ra tu sh+ya hoh zhes dgyes pa'i thal mo lan gsum rdeb /
NK005(ca)003:974: zhes rin po che'i rgyas rnam snang dang /
NK005(ca)003:976: thod pa'i rgyas he ru ka dang /
NK005(ca)003:980: rin po che'i rgyas nyi ma dang /
NK005(ca)003:982: snga ma'i rgya ci rigs pas rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor rnams la dbang bskur ro //
NK005(ca)003:983: de dag ni rnal 'byor chen po zhes bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:984: 'dir dam ye gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor la
NK005(ca)003:985: ji srid mi skyo'i bar du rtse gcig tu bsgom
NK005(ca)003:987: gnyis pa rnal 'byor gyi yan lag la /
NK005(ca)003:993: dang po la phyag dang mchod pa gnyis las /
NK005(ca)003:994: dang po phyag bya ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:995: gus pa'i thal mo sbyar nas //
NK005(ca)003:996: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK005(ca)003:997: phyogs bzhi'i dkyil 'khor dbus rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)003:998: skye 'gro rdul snyed gnas pa kun //
NK005(ca)003:999: bde gshegs lha yi dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK005(ca)003:1000: phyogs dus kun nas tshogs pa'i lha //
NK005(ca)003:1001: gnyis su med par phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1002: +aahh+aum a ti p+au hoh b+han+d+ha ka ro mi gu
NK005(ca)003:1003: ru pa ti a la la hoh zhes phyag bya'o
NK005(ca)003:1004: // gnyis pa mchod pa lnga las /
NK005(ca)003:1005: dang po mchod sprin sprul pa ni //
NK005(ca)003:1007: stong gsum rdul snyed ma lus pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1008: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
NK005(ca)003:1009: lha mo'i tshogs rnams ma lus spro //
NK005(ca)003:1010: me tog bdug pa mar me ma //
NK005(ca)003:1011: dri mchog kun gyis mchod par bya //
NK005(ca)003:1012: pa na pem pe nu su ra to ti pu
NK005(ca)003:1013: pa ra mu sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma
NK005(ca)003:1016: gnyis pa 'bul pa las phyi mchod ni /
NK005(ca)003:1021: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai b+ha ga w+aan /
NK005(ca)003:1024: lha yi me tog shin tu 'bar //
NK005(ca)003:1025: lha yi dri yis nye bar byugs //
NK005(ca)003:1026: me tog bzang po 'di bzhes la //
NK005(ca)003:1027: gnas 'di nyid du bzhugs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1032: bdag la dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1034: tsan+dana gur gum sbyar ba yi //
NK005(ca)003:1035: dri mchog bdug spos dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)003:1036: dbang po'i sgo rnams tshim pa'i mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1037: byin gyis rlob la bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1039: sna tshogs lha yi dri ldan pa //
NK005(ca)003:1040: sna tshogs ga bur gyis ni brgyan //
NK005(ca)003:1041: sna tshogs h+aum las yang dag byung //
NK005(ca)003:1042: dri mchog 'di dag bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1044: kha dog dri dang ro ldan pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1045: bza' ba'i bye brag sna tshogs pa //
NK005(ca)003:1046: zhal zas thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:1047: 'gro ba'i don du bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1049: dpag bsam shing sogs rgyu las byung //
NK005(ca)003:1050: lha yi na bza' khyad par 'phags //
NK005(ca)003:1051: btso ma gser gyi mdog mtshungs dang //
NK005(ca)003:1052: sna tshogs rin chen rgyan sogs 'bul //
NK005(ca)003:1053: badz+ra sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa //
NK005(ca)003:1054: gzhan yang mchod pa rol mo'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:1055: sna tshogs rnam pa du ma dang //
NK005(ca)003:1056: dga' ba'i glu dang dbyangs kyi mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1057: shis pa'i sgra kun gyis kyang mchod //
NK005(ca)003:1060: gsum pa nang gi mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1061: lha so so'i nga rgyal bzung nas /
NK005(ca)003:1062: h+aum zhes skad gsang mtho dman gre 'gyur dang bcas pa'i glu blang ste /
NK005(ca)003:1063: mdzub mo skyil krung du bsnol mthe bos bkab ste
NK005(ca)003:1064: mdzub mo'i rtse mo'i 'bras ltar ston pa rdo rje
NK005(ca)003:1065: sems dpa'i glu'i phyag rgya bcings /
NK005(ca)003:1066: 'di la chos kyi snying po'i gsal kha dang yum sngags kyang logs pa med cing /
NK005(ca)003:1067: yab yum gnyis med kyi phyir /
NK005(ca)003:1068: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa ah dzahh+aum bam hoh su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:1069: zhes gtso bo'i snying po brjod do //
NK005(ca)003:1070: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag cag sgrub la rtogs par mdzad du gsol /
NK005(ca)003:1072: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag nyid bde ba mkha' 'gro sgyu ma'i tshogs rnams bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1073: 'gro ba'i rgyud rnams rnam pa sna tshogs 'dul mchog grub pa bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK005(ca)003:1074: a la la hoh de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyor ba'i rnam pa sna tshogs gang rnams bstan tu gsol /
NK005(ca)003:1075: dzahh+aum bam hoh kye ma bde mchog bde bas bzung
NK005(ca)003:1076: la rnam par sprul h+aum snang bar mdzad du gsol
NK005(ca)003:1077: / a la la hoh de bzhin gshegs pa kun
NK005(ca)003:1078: gyi mkha' 'gro sgyu mas slob ma bzung du gsol
NK005(ca)003:1079: / // rab tu dga' ba rjes su chags pa'i mda' gzhu rab tu phra bas rgyas btab pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1080: rab tu dga' ba'i sbyor ba'i bde bas myos pa'i bde bas thams cad bdag la grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1081: rab tu bde mchog rnam pa sna tshogs rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab bsgrengs pa'i longs spyod dang //
NK005(ca)003:1082: rab tu dga' ba'i dbang phyug che mchog grub pa
NK005(ca)003:1083: de bzhin gshegs pa rab tu sna tshogs bde mchog
NK005(ca)003:1084: rol cig hoh zhes pa ni dpal rdo rje sems
NK005(ca)003:1085: dpa'i glu'o // thal mo khong stong mdzub mo'i rtse
NK005(ca)003:1086: mo bkug ste mthe bong rtse dang sbyar ba rtag
NK005(ca)003:1088: ru ru spu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa ni sarba ar+tha s+aa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:1089: zhes chos kyi snying po lha mo rnams kyi lce la bkod de //
NK005(ca)003:1090: rdo rje sems dpa' bsdus pa na //
NK005(ca)003:1093: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1094: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1095: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1096: dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1097: mchod pa chen po thams cad grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1098: mnyam pa chen po'i gnas la rol du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1100: rdo rje thal mo kha gyen du phye mdzub mo
NK005(ca)003:1101: bkug mthe bong mche ba ltar phyir brkyang ba he
NK005(ca)003:1103: d+hu ba b+ha ga ta ma h+aa de bi hi ri mi ri ni sh+re ya /
NK005(ca)003:1106: rdo rje las kyi mda' gzhu la phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)003:1107: rdo rje chags pa'i dam tshig dpal khyod 'dud //
NK005(ca)003:1108: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rab tu 'jigs la 'dud //
NK005(ca)003:1109: rdo rje dril bu rab tu 'khrol ba'i dpal //
NK005(ca)003:1110: gzigs pa rnam pa sna tshogs 'gyur ba'i rgyas thob la //
NK005(ca)003:1111: rnam pa sna tshogs 'o byed 'khyud pas rmongs mdzad de //
NK005(ca)003:1112: rnam pa sna tshogs bde ba'i mchog brtan kun stsol ma //
NK005(ca)003:1113: rnam pa sna tshogs bde mchog ngo mtshar bstan du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1115: rdo rje thal mo las gung mo rtse sbyar mthe
NK005(ca)003:1116: bong mathe'u chung 'dab ma bzhir byas pa gar dbang
NK005(ca)003:1117: gi rgya dang / t+aa re tut+ta re tu re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:1119: la lar rab tu drag cing skye bo drag la drag pa'i bud med sku ltar snang //
NK005(ca)003:1120: 'gro ba mtha' dag 'dul phyir la lar rab tu snang ba'i 'khor lo phyag na bsnams pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1121: la lar rab tu des shing zhi bar mi 'gyur sbyin pa tshangs pa'i skur yang ston par mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1122: la lar rab tu 'bar ba'i chags la pad+mo'i dam tshig bdag la grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1124: rdo rje thal mo las mdzub mo phyir bkug ste /
NK005(ca)003:1125: de'i rtse mo mthe bos mnan pa rdo rje nyi ma'i rgya dang /
NK005(ca)003:1126: tram ba ba ta ta ta ta ta /
NK005(ca)003:1128: thams cad dbang bskur dbang phyug dam pa mi zad pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1129: gter mchog bdag la grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1130: sku mchog rgyal mtshan rgyal ba bsgreng rdo rje //
NK005(ca)003:1131: rin chen shin tu che ba bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)003:1133: rdo rje thal mo las mathe'u chung srin lag mnyam
NK005(ca)003:1134: par brkyang mdzub mo bkug ste rtse sprad pa rta'i
NK005(ca)003:1136: h+r+aihpad+ma ba da pa mu kha yo gi shwa ra /
NK005(ca)003:1139: la lar mkhas pa'i gzugs kyang 'dzin //
NK005(ca)003:1140: la lar dus mtha'i dus ltar drag /
NK005(ca)003:1141: la lar rgyal ba'i dbang bzhin zhi //
NK005(ca)003:1142: la lar rta mchog sbyor bas grub //
NK005(ca)003:1143: myos byed stong las lhag par bde ba 'dod pa'i gzugs ston pa //
NK005(ca)003:1144: 'dul pa'i dbang gis gshin rje stong las lhag par rab tu 'jigs //
NK005(ca)003:1145: zhi ba'i sku ni tshangs pa stong las lhag par rab tu mdzes //
NK005(ca)003:1146: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog tu de bzhin gshegs kun grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1148: gsum pa bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni //
NK005(ca)003:1149: 'byung ba thams cad lnga las byung //
NK005(ca)003:1150: rang las ma byung gang yang med //
NK005(ca)003:1151: gtsang rme'i dri rtog kun bral ba'i //
NK005(ca)003:1152: bdud rtsi byang chub sems chen po //
NK005(ca)003:1153: bdag sogs gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:1154: mnyam pa chen po'i gnas la rol //
NK005(ca)003:1155: na mahsarba pany+tsa a mri ta +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:1157: kun bzang rigs lnga gsang bdag dri med grags //
NK005(ca)003:1158: in+d+ra b+hu ti u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK005(ca)003:1159: ku ku r+aa dza mu di ta rnams la //
NK005(ca)003:1160: sman mchod 'bul lo mchog thun dngos grub stsol //
NK005(ca)003:1161: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1162: arka so ma badz+ra ba hu ta //
NK005(ca)003:1163: mus to ba hu tahdang gus ko tah dri med bshes gnyen rma lo rin mchog la //
NK005(ca)003:1164: sman mchod sarba mkhas pa'i dbang po gtsug gyer rnam gnyis dang //
NK005(ca)003:1165: tshul khrims byang chub thugs sras rnam pa gsum //
NK005(ca)003:1166: byang chub 'od dang blo gros rgyal mtshan la //
NK005(ca)003:1167: sman mchod sarba rin chen tshul khrims rong ston chos bzang dang //
NK005(ca)003:1168: yam shud blo bzang 'gos ston zla ba 'bar //
NK005(ca)003:1169: zla ba 'bum grags dngos grub rgyal mtshan la //
NK005(ca)003:1170: sman mchod sarba 'gos ston chos rdor 'gos pa dngos grub mgon //
NK005(ca)003:1171: dbus pa sangs 'bum gser steng chos 'od bzang //
NK005(ca)003:1172: mi bskyod rdo rje mkhan chen bsod 'phel la //
NK005(ca)003:1173: sman mchod sarba bag ston tshul rgya bla chen bsod nams dpal //
NK005(ca)003:1174: 'jam dbyangs kun blo nam mkha' tshul khrims dang //
NK005(ca)003:1175: rong pa blo bzang mkhyen rab chos rje la //
NK005(ca)003:1176: sman mchod sarba sam b+ha sh+r+ai tshul khrims 'od zer 'bar //
NK005(ca)003:1177: bsod nams dpal 'byor rin chen bkra shis sde //
NK005(ca)003:1178: blo gsal rgya mtsho 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse la //
NK005(ca)003:1179: sman mchod sarba dbang phyug rab brtan bsod nams mchog ldan dpal //
NK005(ca)003:1180: ngag dbang o rgyan rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK005(ca)003:1181: 'gyur med rgya mtsho rin chen rnam rgyal la //
NK005(ca)003:1182: sman mchod sarba o rgyan bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK005(ca)003:1183: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i zhabs //
NK005(ca)003:1184: bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer la //
NK005(ca)003:1185: sman mchod sarba brgyud srol kun 'dus rtsa ba'i bla ma dang //
NK005(ca)003:1186: bde gshegs sgyu ma bde mchog yi dam lha //
NK005(ca)003:1187: ma sring mkha' 'gro dam can rgya mtsho la //
NK005(ca)003:1188: sman mchod sarba pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1191: sman mchod brgyud 'debs ltar kha bsgyur dz+ny+aa nas so //
NK005(ca)003:1193: bzhi pa rak+ta'i mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1194: h+aum mdzad kyi he ru ka'i sgrubs thabs las /
NK005(ca)003:1195: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK005(ca)003:1196: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK005(ca)003:1197: dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK005(ca)003:1198: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK005(ca)003:1199: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1200: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK005(ca)003:1202: ma lus bzhes nas bsnams su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1203: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa rak+ta kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1205: lnga pa gsang ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1206: byin rlabs mtshan dang rgyan ldan pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1207: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1208: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)003:1209: gsang ba chen po rnam par rol //
NK005(ca)003:1210: ma h+aa su kha bo d+hi tsit+ta a la la hoh zhes mchod /
NK005(ca)003:1212: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid can //
NK005(ca)003:1213: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1214: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub thams cad sbyin mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)003:1215: dri med mi g.yo mnyam med dam pa'i chos mchog can //
NK005(ca)003:1216: yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la'ang tshad med de //
NK005(ca)003:1217: dpe ni nam mkha' dang yang bskrun du yod ma yin //
NK005(ca)003:1218: dngos grub mtha' yas mnyam med dpe dang bral ba rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1219: sems can khams la dngos grub mchog rnams nges par stsol //
NK005(ca)003:1220: rtag tu dri ma med pa thugs rje'i shugs las byung //
NK005(ca)003:1221: smon lam grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
NK005(ca)003:1222: 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
NK005(ca)003:1223: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
NK005(ca)003:1224: tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu rdzogs pa yi //
NK005(ca)003:1225: bde bar gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes gyur kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1226: khams gsum dag la dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad pa yi //
NK005(ca)003:1227: thugs rje'i spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yongs mi 'gyur //
NK005(ca)003:1229: shin tu bzang po'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NK005(ca)003:1230: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang nas go 'phang mchog brnyes pa //
NK005(ca)003:1231: khams gsum kun la rtag tu dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1232: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa //
NK005(ca)003:1233: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)003:1234: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK005(ca)003:1235: yang dag yon tan rgya chen te //
NK005(ca)003:1236: lan cig tsam zhig brjod pas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1238: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du bzhugs pa rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1239: bcad gtub sdug bsngal lus la byung bar mi 'gyur yang //
NK005(ca)003:1240: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas //
NK005(ca)003:1241: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong ba'i mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1242: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK005(ca)003:1243: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'byung ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1244: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK005(ca)003:1245: re smon thams cad dus 'di nyid du stsal du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1250: skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:1252: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar dmigs nas /
NK005(ca)003:1253: b+h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+ha dz+ny+aa na man+da la phata dzah zhes dang /
NK005(ca)003:1254: h+aum hi h+r+aihtram phata dzah zhes btags pas dam tshig
NK005(ca)003:1255: gi 'khor lo las ye shes kyi 'khor lo rten
NK005(ca)003:1256: dang brten par bcas pa logs su phye nas mdun
NK005(ca)003:1257: gyi nam mkhar bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)003:1259: bdag mdun gyi dkyil 'khor sems dpa' sum brtsegs kyi
NK005(ca)003:1260: sku gsung thugs sa bon gsum gyis mtshan pa thabs
NK005(ca)003:1261: dang shes rab kyi phreng ba gnyis dang ldan par
NK005(ca)003:1262: gyur pa la / sngags zlos pa'i tshe /
NK005(ca)003:1263: bdag gi thugs ka nas sngags kyi 'od zer mchod pa'i tshul du spros pas /
NK005(ca)003:1264: ye shes kyi lha tshogs rnams dgyes pa bskyed /
NK005(ca)003:1266: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams
NK005(ca)003:1267: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam par bdag la
NK005(ca)003:1268: stsal zhing thim par dmigs te /
NK005(ca)003:1269: dam ye 'phro 'du gsal ba gsum dang ldan pa
NK005(ca)003:1270: gtso 'khor thams cad la sbyar nas skyon bcu spangs
NK005(ca)003:1271: te bazla'o // bzla bya'i sngags ni /
NK005(ca)003:1272: badz+ra sa t+wa ma h+aa sa ma ya +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK005(ca)003:1273: zhes thun mong gi yi ge bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:1274: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aahdzahh+aum bam hoh su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)003:1275: zhes thun mong min pa rdor sems kyi snying po'i yi ge bco brgyad pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:1279: he ru ka badz+ra sa ma ya h+r+aih sarba dush+tana
NK005(ca)003:1280: sa ma ya mu dra pra b+hany+dza ka h'u phata
NK005(ca)003:1282: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+harma nirte shwa ra h+r+aihdzah gar dbang gi'o //
NK005(ca)003:1285: sid+d+h+ya ma h+aa badz+ra rat+na ba ba ta ta tram /
NK005(ca)003:1289: khyad par gyi bzlas pa la sogs pa ni man ngag las shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1290: gsum pa skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba la /
NK005(ca)003:1291: mchod bstod bshags pa ye shes bsdu ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:1293: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK005(ca)003:1298: badz+ra g+airti h+r+aih badz+ra nirti +aah a la la hoh zhes mchod nas /
NK005(ca)003:1300: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)003:1301: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1303: che ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK005(ca)003:1304: 'khor ba'i nyes pas ma gos shing //
NK005(ca)003:1305: 'gro la rjes su chags pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1306: zla ba ltar dkar rtsa dmar 'gying //
NK005(ca)003:1307: rdor sems bde ba che la bdud //
NK005(ca)003:1308: stong pa ma yin mi stong min //
NK005(ca)003:1309: dbu ma'i lam la rab 'jog pa //
NK005(ca)003:1310: gti mug rgya mtsho zhi bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1311: rgyal ba rtag pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)003:1312: shin tu gdul dka' drag po la //
NK005(ca)003:1313: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur bas //
NK005(ca)003:1314: de bzhin gshegs kun khro bor 'gyur //
NK005(ca)003:1316: chags chen rdo rje chos kyi sku //
NK005(ca)003:1317: lta ba ngan rnams sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:1318: sgyu ma sna tshogs tshul ston pa //
NK005(ca)003:1320: yid bzhin nor bu sbyin pa po //
NK005(ca)003:1321: ser sna zil gnon 'gro ba sgrol //
NK005(ca)003:1322: bsam pa thams cad rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)003:1323: rdo rje nyi ma la phyag 'tshal //
NK005(ca)003:1324: rdo rje las ni brtson 'grus che //
NK005(ca)003:1325: khro dang nga rgyal le lo 'joms //
NK005(ca)003:1326: pha rol gnon pa shin tu stobs //
NK005(ca)003:1327: rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1328: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba che //
NK005(ca)003:1329: snying po'i ye shes kun tu ston //
NK005(ca)003:1330: mnyam nyid gsang ba chen po'i dbyings //
NK005(ca)003:1332: 'gro kun sgyu ma bde mchog la //
NK005(ca)003:1333: bde ba chen po'i ting 'dzin sbyor //
NK005(ca)003:1334: lha mo lhan cig spyod rnams la //
NK005(ca)003:1335: rab tu dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1336: sems can tshogs rnams yongs sbyang phyir //
NK005(ca)003:1337: rjes su 'brang ba lha mo'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1338: bde ba'i gar gyis rol mdzad pa //
NK005(ca)003:1339: lha mo de rnams la yang 'dud //
NK005(ca)003:1340: mi bzad rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK005(ca)003:1341: bla med mchod pas rnam 'phrul ba //
NK005(ca)003:1342: mchod pa'i lha mo thams cad la //
NK005(ca)003:1343: tshogs gnyis bsgrub phyir phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1344: dgug gzhug la sogs las mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)003:1345: phrin las thams cad sgrub pa po //
NK005(ca)003:1346: sgo skyong gnas pa thams cad la //
NK005(ca)003:1347: rtag tu gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1348: phyi rol gnas pa'i dam can tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:1349: sgrub la rtag tu phan par brtson //
NK005(ca)003:1350: gzhan yang dur khrod gnas rnams la //
NK005(ca)003:1351: rab dang sems kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1352: ye shes las grub gzhal med khang //
NK005(ca)003:1353: bdud bzhi'i stobs ni 'phrog byed pa //
NK005(ca)003:1354: srung ba'i 'khor lor bcas rnams la //
NK005(ca)003:1355: rab tu gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1358: ye nas gnyis med chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)003:1359: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK005(ca)003:1360: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK005(ca)003:1361: de ldog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK005(ca)003:1362: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK005(ca)003:1363: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur pas //
NK005(ca)003:1364: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK005(ca)003:1365: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1368: h+aum zhes brjod pas dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chu
NK005(ca)003:1369: la chu bzhag pa ltar dbyer med du gyur par
NK005(ca)003:1370: bsam la yig brgya brjod pas brtan par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1371: bzhi pa thig le'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK005(ca)003:1372: sna rtser thig le phra zhing phra bar bsam pa
NK005(ca)003:1373: la phyi'i dkyil 'khor bsdus te ji srid mtshan ma
NK005(ca)003:1374: lnga mthong gi bar du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK005(ca)003:1376: sngar bzhin rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i gsang ba'i
NK005(ca)003:1377: rdo rje yum gyi mkhar rol pa'i rtse mor h+aum
NK005(ca)003:1378: yig shin tu dkar ba'i rang bzhin can gsal bar
NK005(ca)003:1379: dmigs la / de'i 'od zer gyis rang 'dra'i sku
NK005(ca)003:1380: gnyis pa spros pas nam mkha'i khams thams cad khyab
NK005(ca)003:1381: dmigs la / par byas / slar 'dus h+aum la
NK005(ca)003:1382: thim pas dri ma med pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK005(ca)003:1383: brtan par bsgoms la ji srid mtshan ma lnga mthong
NK005(ca)003:1385: lnga pa phra mo'i rnal 'byor ni /
NK005(ca)003:1386: snying gar dbyangs gsal bcu drug po tshan gsum bskor
NK005(ca)003:1387: ba'i dbus su a yig zla phyed thig ler ldan
NK005(ca)003:1388: pa'am phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rnam pa
NK005(ca)003:1389: shin tu phra ba la mtshan ma lnga mthong gi
NK005(ca)003:1390: bar du bsgom par bshad do //
NK005(ca)003:1391: gnyis pa la mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor dang dag dran gnyis las /
NK005(ca)003:1394: mnyam nyid dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1395: don dam bde ba chen po'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1396: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes kyi //
NK005(ca)003:1397: lha nyid brtson pas bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)003:1398: zhes pas chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi dkyil
NK005(ca)003:1399: 'khor du don dam bde ba chen po'i sku gzung
NK005(ca)003:1400: 'dzin gyi mtshan ma thams cad dang bral ba de
NK005(ca)003:1401: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings dang ye shes kyi lha dbyer
NK005(ca)003:1402: med pa la rtse gcig tu mnyam par 'jog go
NK005(ca)003:1404: rten ni dge ba bcu yin te //
NK005(ca)003:1405: gru bzhi bden pa bzhi ru brjod //
NK005(ca)003:1406: yan lag bcu gnyis rdo rje'i rwa //
NK005(ca)003:1407: yon tan sna tshogs kun rgyas shing //
NK005(ca)003:1408: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi khyab mdzad zur //
NK005(ca)003:1409: chos rdzogs sum cu rtsa bdun las //
NK005(ca)003:1411: rang bzhin ye shes drug dag pas //
NK005(ca)003:1412: rigs kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1413: rnam thar brgyad po ka bar bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1414: rdo rje theg pa'i tshul nyid mdzes //
NK005(ca)003:1415: mnyam nyid dkyil 'khor chen por brjod //
NK005(ca)003:1416: thugs rje chen po'i char phab bo //
NK005(ca)003:1417: zhes rten gyi rnam dag dang /
NK005(ca)003:1418: nyon mongs drug rnams rnam dag pa //
NK005(ca)003:1419: de las ye shes drug 'dzin pa //
NK005(ca)003:1420: rigs drug 'khor los sgyur ba ste //
NK005(ca)003:1421: rdo rje'i sems dpa' gcig pu'i ngang //
NK005(ca)003:1422: rtog pas ma gos thugs rje'i bdag /
NK005(ca)003:1423: zla 'dra dmar ba'i mdangs dang ldan //
NK005(ca)003:1424: khams sogs spyod pa rnam dag cing //
NK005(ca)003:1425: thugs rje'i sprul pa rgya chen po //
NK005(ca)003:1426: lha mo'i tshogs rnams dgod byas nas //
NK005(ca)003:1427: nyon mongs nyi shu dag par mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1428: ye shes snang ba bsam yas pas //
NK005(ca)003:1429: sna tshogs dkyil 'khor cir yang snang //
NK005(ca)003:1430: zhes brten pa'i rnam dag bsam pa ste /
NK005(ca)003:1431: de dag ni dngos gzhi'i cho ga'o //
NK005(ca)003:1432: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK005(ca)003:1438: spyod lam gyi rnal 'byor dang drug go //
NK005(ca)003:1439: dang po tshogs mchod la lnga las /
NK005(ca)003:1440: dang po bsham zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1441: dam rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad rnams bshams nas bsang chu dang bdud rtsis bran la /
NK005(ca)003:1442: ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sarba d+r+wa byam sho d+ha ya +aahh+aum gis bsang /
NK005(ca)003:1443: ram yam kham gis dngos 'dzin nyes skyon thams cad bsregs gtor bkrus te dag par byas /
NK005(ca)003:1444: stong pa'i ngang las tshogs gzhong pad+ma 'bar ba'i snod
NK005(ca)003:1445: du tshogs rdzas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'dod yon
NK005(ca)003:1446: gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa so so'i
NK005(ca)003:1447: lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin
NK005(ca)003:1448: 'phro ba'i longs spyod kyi gter du gyur par bsam
NK005(ca)003:1450: lan gsum brjod pas byin gyis brlab /
NK005(ca)003:1451: gnyis pa tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:1452: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pa khyab pa'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1453: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1454: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK005(ca)003:1455: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1456: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa ka ru
NK005(ca)003:1457: ni ka dri sh+ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes spyan
NK005(ca)003:1458: drangs / gsum pa mchod pa la gnyis kyi dang po spyir mchod pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1459: +aahh+aum su ra to u pa b+h+yah ka ma la
NK005(ca)003:1460: m+aa la ya badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na
NK005(ca)003:1461: pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga w+aan dzahmh'u bam hoh a la
NK005(ca)003:1462: la hoh pa na pem pe nu su ra to
NK005(ca)003:1463: ti bu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK005(ca)003:1464: sid+d+hi huh sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa
NK005(ca)003:1465: su kha sid+d+hi huh zhes dang /
NK005(ca)003:1466: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1467: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1469: dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1470: mchod pa chen po thams cad dag par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1476: dri'i phyag rgya rnams bcings te mchod cing /
NK005(ca)003:1477: spron su ra to bcu drug gis kyang mchod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1478: gnyis pa bye brag tu mchod pa la gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:1479: tshogs phud cha gsum mam bzhir spros te /
NK005(ca)003:1481: cha dang po stegs la bkod /
NK005(ca)003:1482: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)003:1483: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK005(ca)003:1484: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK005(ca)003:1485: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1486: zhes 'dod yon drug gi mchod pas dgyes shing tshim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)003:1488: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK005(ca)003:1489: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK005(ca)003:1490: sems can dbang gis nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK005(ca)003:1491: mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK005(ca)003:1492: zhes dang yi ge brgya pa brjod /
NK005(ca)003:1494: ling+ga logs su bcas pa med na tshogs zan cha
