NK005(ca)003:1495: gsum pa de'i 'dod yon gyi lha mo rang la
NK005(ca)003:1496: bsdus nas / badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ko&a ham /
NK005(ca)003:1497: bdag nyid rta mchog he ru ka'i skur gyur /
NK005(ca)003:1499: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1500: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1501: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1502: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1503: bcom ldan 'das sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor
NK005(ca)003:1504: ba 'khor los sgyur ba drug gi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK005(ca)003:1505: lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1506: sprul pa yang sprul bka' sdod phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1507: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis ma rungs
NK005(ca)003:1508: pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa thams
NK005(ca)003:1509: cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par
NK005(ca)003:1510: gyur cig / n+ri yam dzah n+ri badz+ra am ku
NK005(ca)003:1511: sha dzah trihyam dzah tri badz+ra am ku sha dzah
NK005(ca)003:1512: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas bkug la /
NK005(ca)003:1513: dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug bcings bsdams nas myos par byas te /
NK005(ca)003:1514: mgon med skyabs bral rnam par 'gyur ba'i tshul du gnas pa la /
NK005(ca)003:1515: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK005(ca)003:1516: mtshon cha sna tshogs pa'i char du phab pa dmigs
NK005(ca)003:1517: bya la phog / dug lnga ye shes lngar sbyangs /
NK005(ca)003:1518: dwangs ma h+aum du gyur pa 'og min du spar bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)003:1519: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra
NK005(ca)003:1520: sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu dra ma ti kha
NK005(ca)003:1521: kha kh+aa hi hri da ya pi pa h+aum phata
NK005(ca)003:1523: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK005(ca)003:1524: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1525: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:1526: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK005(ca)003:1527: sarba dush+tana m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK005(ca)003:1528: ces phur bus gdab cing ral gris gtub pa dang tho bas brdung ba rnams byas la /
NK005(ca)003:1529: sha khrag bdud rtsir spar ba stob cing /
NK005(ca)003:1530: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK005(ca)003:1535: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kha le le le h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK005(ca)003:1537: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1538: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:1539: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK005(ca)003:1540: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK005(ca)003:1541: gar bya sgrub po rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)003:1542: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK005(ca)003:1543: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK005(ca)003:1544: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1545: me tog la sogs tsan+dana phreng //
NK005(ca)003:1546: bzang dgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK005(ca)003:1547: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1548: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK005(ca)003:1549: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK005(ca)003:1550: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1551: ces stob pas dgyes par byas la /
NK005(ca)003:1552: ma h+aa su kha badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes rdor sems su nga rgyal 'phos te /
NK005(ca)003:1554: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK005(ca)003:1555: ston ka'i zla zhal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)003:1556: bcom ldan bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK005(ca)003:1557: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK005(ca)003:1558: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngams pa'i tshogs dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1559: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK005(ca)003:1560: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK005(ca)003:1561: bzhes te a la la yis dgyes par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1565: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK005(ca)003:1566: pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes 'khor gsum bde ba chen por
NK005(ca)003:1567: ro mnyam mo // bzhi pa tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK005(ca)003:1568: brda dang brda'i 'bul len sogs spyi dang 'dra bar
NK005(ca)003:1569: byas nas 'dod pa lnga ldan du longs spyod do
NK005(ca)003:1570: // lnga pa lhag ma'i cho ga ni gtor chog dang gnad gcig pas sbrel te shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1571: gnyis pa gtor ma'i cho ga la /
NK005(ca)003:1573: mgron dgugs shing dbang du bya ba /
NK005(ca)003:1574: mchod pa'i las rim dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)003:1576: lhag ma rnams snod gcig tu bsdus pa'i rme gtor dang /
NK005(ca)003:1577: sngar zur du bcad pa'i phud dang mchod pa'i ras ma rnams dang /
NK005(ca)003:1578: sha chang sogs bza' btung sna tshogs pa'i gtor ma gsar pa'ang thod pa'i snod du blug pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1579: spos dang me tog sogs longs spyod kyi yo byad
NK005(ca)003:1580: sna tshogs pa rnams phyi rol du man+dala zla gam
NK005(ca)003:1581: dmar po'i dbus su rigs lnga'i thig le lnga byas
NK005(ca)003:1583: mchod pa thun mong ba'i byin rlabs spyi mthun dang /
NK005(ca)003:1584: khyad par bdud rtsi byin rlabs sngar bshad pa bzhin byas nas /
NK005(ca)003:1585: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba las /
NK005(ca)003:1586: khyad par gtor ma'i gnas su /
NK005(ca)003:1587: ma h+aa tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK005(ca)003:1588: man+dala gyi dbus su ham las byung ba'i rdo rje rta mchog /
NK005(ca)003:1589: de'i mdun du lha chen po /
NK005(ca)003:1593: de'i phyi rol shar phyogs su phyogs skyong dang zhing skyong /
NK005(ca)003:1594: lho phyogs su ma mo'i tshogs /
NK005(ca)003:1595: nub phyogs su lha chen po rnams dang klu chen brgyad /
NK005(ca)003:1596: byang du 'byung po sna tshogs pa dang 'gro ba
NK005(ca)003:1597: rigs drug gi gtso bo 'khor bcas gnas par gyur
NK005(ca)003:1599: rang nyid rta mchog gi skur sprul pa'i snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK005(ca)003:1600: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gtor mgron
NK005(ca)003:1601: gyi lha tshogs thams cad spyan drangs par bsam la
NK005(ca)003:1603: badz+ra t+aa ki n+ai b+h+yah e a ral+li hring hring dzahdzah zhes dang spyugs pa'i brdas spyan drangs /
NK005(ca)003:1604: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK005(ca)003:1605: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya phata
NK005(ca)003:1606: / ces dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan pas dbang du 'dus shing bka' nod par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)003:1607: gsum pa la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK005(ca)003:1612: gan+d+ham p+au dza s+pha ra na ar+g+ham ba lim ta kha kha zhes mchod /
NK005(ca)003:1614: gtsang phud kyi ras ma dme gtor du blugs pa
NK005(ca)003:1615: la pad+ma'i rgyas byang sems kyi kha phru btab nas
NK005(ca)003:1616: / gu ru kro d+h+aa rat+na sa ma ya sh+r+ai
NK005(ca)003:1617: sha pur+wa bud+d+ha k+she tra p+aa la k+sho b+ha ka
NK005(ca)003:1618: / ra h+aum phata / ces pas byin gyis brlabs la /
NK005(ca)003:1619: 'khor los sgyur ba drug gi sngags mthar /
NK005(ca)003:1620: i dam ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1621: zhes btags pas 'jig rten las 'das pa la phul /
NK005(ca)003:1623: 'jig rten kun gtso mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1624: 'jigs byed drag po stobs ldan pa //
NK005(ca)003:1625: bde gshegs sras sogs bran mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1626: byang chub sems ldan snying rje can //
NK005(ca)003:1627: dbang phyug chen po chung mar bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1628: de bzhin khyab 'jug tshangs pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:1629: brgya byin 'dod dga' chung mar bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1630: lha chen 'khor bcas tshogs rnams dang //
NK005(ca)003:1631: phyogs skyong brgyad po 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1632: klu chen brgyad po 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1634: dur khrod ma mo'i tshogs bcas dang //
NK005(ca)003:1635: gzhan yang lha srin sde brgyad dang //
NK005(ca)003:1637: sku gsung thugs sogs sbyangs byas nas //
NK005(ca)003:1638: rang gi lha yi gzugs 'dzin rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1640: mchod gtor rgyan dang bcas pa bzhes //
NK005(ca)003:1641: dam tshig srungs shig dam tshig can //
NK005(ca)003:1642: las la brtson pa'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:1644: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK005(ca)003:1645: las mdzad rdo rje bran bcas pas //
NK005(ca)003:1646: zhi rgyas dbang drag las sgrub cing //
NK005(ca)003:1647: theg chen gsang sngags bsrung ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1648: nad dang gdon sogs zhi ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1649: tshe dbang bkra shis spel ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1650: bde legs 'bras bu sgrub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1651: +aahh+aum pad+ma ba ta ba mu kha h+aum h+r+aih zhes
NK005(ca)003:1652: rta'i rgyas dngos grub dbang du byas nas rdo rje'i
NK005(ca)003:1653: thal mo gyen du phyes la /
NK005(ca)003:1654: bud+d+ha d+aa ki n+ai nam ba lim ta pra t+aits+tsha phata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1655: de bzhin du badz+ra d+aa ki n+ai nam ba ling+ta pra t+aits+tsha h+aum phata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1656: rat+na d+aa ki n+ai nam ba ling+ta pra t+aits+tsha t+r+aam phata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1657: pad+ma d+aa ki n+ai nam ba ling+ta pra t+aits+tsha h+r+aihphata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1658: karma d+aa ki n+ai nam ba ling+ta pra t+aits+tsha hohphata kh+aa hi /
NK005(ca)003:1659: zhes lan gsum gyis mgron spyi la phul nas /
NK005(ca)003:1660: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas te //
NK005(ca)003:1661: thugs rje chen pos gzigs nas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1662: sna tshogs rgyud rnams sprul mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1663: gar mkhan 'khor lo'i rgyud mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)003:1664: drag po zhi mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1665: sna tshogs gar gyis rnam par sprul la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1666: rdo rje la sogs mtshon chas rol la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1667: ma lus lha yi lha mchog skyong la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1668: dpa' bo rtsal rdzogs stobs bcu'i shugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1669: a ti p+au hoh a la la hoh zhes gsol nas /
NK005(ca)003:1670: gats+tsha muhzhesa phyi 'khor gyi mgron rnams rang gnas su gshegs la gtor ma phyi dor /
NK005(ca)003:1671: h+aum zhes ye shes kyi mgron rnams rang gi snying gar bsdu'o //
NK005(ca)003:1672: tshogs mchod dang ma 'brel na gtor chog rang rkyang gi gtor ma man+dala dang bcas pa bshams nas /
NK005(ca)003:1673: kha phrus byin gyis brlab pa sogs sgos chos rnams dor la gzhan cho ga sngar bzhin bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1674: gnyis pa brtan ma skyong ba ni /
NK005(ca)003:1675: phyi rol du brtan pa'i gtor ma sman phudakyisa bran la /
NK005(ca)003:1677: ces brjod pas gtor ma'i rdul phra rab re re
NK005(ca)003:1678: bzhin rin po che'i gur khang longs spyod zad mi
NK005(ca)003:1679: shes pas nam mkha' gang bar bsams la /
NK005(ca)003:1682: tshogs dang bka' yi tshogs bcas nyid //
NK005(ca)003:1683: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK005(ca)003:1684: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1685: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1686: bdag nyid chen mo la sogs bdud mo bzhi //
NK005(ca)003:1687: gangs dkar sha med la sogs gnod sbyin bzhi //
NK005(ca)003:1688: kong btsun de mo la sogs sman mo bzhi //
NK005(ca)003:1689: bod khams skyong ba'i che zhe chen mo rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1690: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1691: lhab lhub mang po'i rgyan dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1692: sil snyan mang po'i sgra dang bcas //
NK005(ca)003:1693: 'dir spyon dam skongs phrin las mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1694: che zhe chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1695: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK005(ca)003:1697: rlangs chen dpal gyi seng+ge yis //
NK005(ca)003:1698: zhing chen stan la bkod nas kyang //
NK005(ca)003:1699: lag tu rdo rje gtad nas ni //
NK005(ca)003:1700: dbang skur gsang ba'i mtshan nas brjod //
NK005(ca)003:1701: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK005(ca)003:1702: bod khams srung zhig skyong ba dang //
NK005(ca)003:1703: rnal 'byor sgrub pa'i grogs bya zhes //
NK005(ca)003:1704: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK005(ca)003:1705: g.yar dam gnyan po rjes dgongs la //
NK005(ca)003:1706: dam rdzas bka' yi gtor ma longs //
NK005(ca)003:1707: bcol ba'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1713: ma ma sring 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:1715: ma h+aa pany+tsa sogs sman raka gtor gsum gyis mchod cing /
NK005(ca)003:1717: brtan ma bcu gnyis 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis
NK005(ca)003:1718: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa srungs sogs kyis phrin las
NK005(ca)003:1719: bcol / ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol nas gtor ma gtsang sar bskyal lo //
NK005(ca)003:1721: skabs 'dir mchod bstod nongs bshags yod med ji ltar yang rung ba las /
NK005(ca)003:1722: yi ge brgya pa brjod pa'i mthar //
NK005(ca)003:1723: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i mtha' klas par //
NK005(ca)003:1724: sems can kun gyi don sgrub pa //
NK005(ca)003:1725: ji ltar thugs kyi dbang phyug bzhin //
NK005(ca)003:1726: de nyid spyod par bdag gyur cig /
NK005(ca)003:1727: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK005(ca)003:1728: sems can thams cad skyon med pa //
NK005(ca)003:1729: gang gi lam gyis grol 'gyur ba //
NK005(ca)003:1730: de yis sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK005(ca)003:1732: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)003:1735: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu'o //
NK005(ca)003:1736: nyal ba'am mthun mtshams la 'jug pa na /
NK005(ca)003:1737: h+aum zhes pas rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyis phog
NK005(ca)003:1738: pas dag pa'i snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang
NK005(ca)003:1740: 'khor rnams rim bzhin gtso bo yab yum la /
NK005(ca)003:1742: de ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK005(ca)003:1743: de ting 'dzin sems dpa' h+aum la /
NK005(ca)003:1744: h+aum gyen rdzogs na da'i bar du bsdus nas mi dmigs par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1745: nyal ba las langs pa'am spyod lam la 'jug pa na /
NK005(ca)003:1746: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa mtshan dpe gsal rdzogs kyi skur ldang ngo //
NK005(ca)003:1747: bzhi pa go bgo lus bsrung ni /
NK005(ca)003:1748: rang gi spyi bo la sogs pa'i gnas bzhir kam ham am trum rnams kyis mtshan bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)003:1749: trum zhes khu tshur gyi rgyas gnas bzhir reg la /
NK005(ca)003:1750: rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa phata lam a ba lam bam h+aum /
NK005(ca)003:1751: zhes rigs lnga'i cod pan gyis dbu brgyan par bsam /
NK005(ca)003:1752: badz+ra tush+t+ya hoh zhes thal mos brtan par bya zhing /
NK005(ca)003:1753: dge ba bsngo ba dang shis pa brjod pa rnams kyis mtha' rgyas par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1754: lnga pa spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor ni /
NK005(ca)003:1755: spyod lam kun tu ma nyams par //
NK005(ca)003:1756: lha nyid du ni bsgom par bya //
NK005(ca)003:1757: dbang po'i snang ba yul dus kun //
NK005(ca)003:1758: dkyil 'khor rol ba'i tshul du brtag /
NK005(ca)003:1760: snod bcud gzhal yas khang dang lhar shes bas dbang
NK005(ca)003:1761: po'i snang ba yul dus thams cad dkyil 'khor rol
NK005(ca)003:1762: pa'i tshul du rnam par dag pa'i zin cing rgyas
NK005(ca)003:1765: bza' btung byin rlabs ma nyams bzlas //
NK005(ca)003:1766: sgyu ma ye shes gnyis med rol //
NK005(ca)003:1767: byed spyod tshogs gnyis rgyu ru brtag /
NK005(ca)003:1768: thams cad 'gro ba'i don du spyad //
NK005(ca)003:1769: ces pas bza' btung bdud rtsir byas nas sgyu ma
NK005(ca)003:1770: lta bur gnyis med du rol zhig bya spyod thams
NK005(ca)003:1771: cad tshogs gnyis kyi rgyu sems can gyi don du
NK005(ca)003:1773: spyi don gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK005(ca)003:1775: des grub pa'i tshad bstan pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:1777: skal ba dang ldan pas tshogs gnyis cig car rdzogs
NK005(ca)003:1778: pa'i lam rgyal ba rnams kyis yul la sbyor ba'i
NK005(ca)003:1779: ched du bla ma mnyes par byas nas zhal gyi
NK005(ca)003:1781: de yang las dang po bas ni /
NK005(ca)003:1782: bsam gtan gyi mi mthun phyogs sgo gsum gyi rnam
NK005(ca)003:1783: par g.yeng ba spangs nas skyo ba'i mtshan nyid bsam
NK005(ca)003:1784: par bya ste / kye ma rang bzhin lta rmongs rnams //
NK005(ca)003:1785: glo bur rtog pas kun tu bslad //
NK005(ca)003:1786: de bzhin yun ring goms shugs las //
NK005(ca)003:1787: bde sdug gnyis tshogs dbang spyod pas //
NK005(ca)003:1788: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs tshogs su snang //
NK005(ca)003:1789: zhes sogs gsungs pas bzhin nges 'byung gis rgyud dag par bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)003:1790: de nas bskyed pa'i rim pa la bslab pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)003:1791: sbyor ba bzhi yi rim pa yis //
NK005(ca)003:1792: de yi lam la rab tu sbyor //
NK005(ca)003:1793: zhes rnal 'byor bzhi ldan du bsgom par gsungs te /
NK005(ca)003:1794: bdag nyid che ba'i lhar sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)003:1795: bdag la bdag gis rab tu mchod //
NK005(ca)003:1797: rnal 'byor thams cad bde ba yis //
NK005(ca)003:1798: rjes su sbyor bas mchod byed cing //
NK005(ca)003:1800: rgyud la myang bar byed pas na //
NK005(ca)003:1803: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyis //
NK005(ca)003:1804: ra s+aa ya na'i bde ba ni //
NK005(ca)003:1805: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dpal dang //
NK005(ca)003:1806: nad med lang tsho bde mchog 'grub //
NK005(ca)003:1807: ces rnal 'byor chen po ste rim pa dang po'i lam dang /
NK005(ca)003:1809: snang bde mnyam pa'i don gnas na //
NK005(ca)003:1810: sku gsum gnyis su med pa'i lam //
NK005(ca)003:1811: grol lam thabs la brten pa dag /
NK005(ca)003:1812: bde ba'i ye shes rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:1813: rtsa rlung so so'i thun mong gi //
NK005(ca)003:1814: nyams myong bskyed par bya ba yin //
NK005(ca)003:1815: zhes rdzogs pa'i rim pa bsgom pa'i tshul ji ltar
NK005(ca)003:1816: gsungs pa bzhin du blo'i nus pa dang sbyar te
NK005(ca)003:1817: nyams su len pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1819: de lta bu'i lam la bslabs te nan tan du
NK005(ca)003:1820: goms par byas pa las tshe 'di la rig pa
NK005(ca)003:1822: de la brten nas mchog gi dngos grub kyang thob par byed do //
NK005(ca)003:1823: de yang 'dir rig 'dzin rnam pa bdun te /
NK005(ca)003:1830: bya ba mthar pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK005(ca)003:1831: de'i sgo nas sngags kyi spyod pa spyad pas dngos
NK005(ca)003:1832: grub kyi mchog mi slob pa'i sa drug rim pa
NK005(ca)003:1833: bzhin du sbyangs pas cig car thob par 'gyur ro
NK005(ca)003:1835: sangs rgyas kyi sa kun tu 'od dang /
NK005(ca)003:1837: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1840: bde ba chen po'i sa rnams so //
NK005(ca)003:1842: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yi rim pa yis //
NK005(ca)003:1843: 'dod pa'i don la rab sbyor zhing //
NK005(ca)003:1844: de dag dang ni dga' spyad na //
NK005(ca)003:1846: rigs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba yi //
NK005(ca)003:1847: gtso bo gang yang rung ba 'grub //
NK005(ca)003:1849: des ni bde ba chen po 'grub //
NK005(ca)003:1851: rig 'dzin rnam pa bdun gyis ni //
NK005(ca)003:1852: rang gi ye shes gnas sbyong zhing //
NK005(ca)003:1853: gsang sngags mthun pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK005(ca)003:1854: mes pa'i blo dang don mthun ston //
NK005(ca)003:1855: rnam grol zag med sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)003:1856: mthar phyin 'di yis thob par byed //
NK005(ca)003:1859: ye shes bla ma'i sa non nas //
NK005(ca)003:1860: zag med rtag tu bde bas zhugs //
NK005(ca)003:1862: de lta bu'i rim pas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK005(ca)003:1863: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i sgo nas //
NK005(ca)003:1864: sgrub pa rnam bdun las la 'jug /
NK005(ca)003:1865: tshogs sgrub phyag rgya'i sgrub pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:1866: rdzas dang sman dang mngon shes dang //
NK005(ca)003:1867: rig 'dzin sgrub pa phyag rgya che //
NK005(ca)003:1868: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:1869: 'dir skabs don nyer mkho'i shes byed cung zad brjod na /
NK005(ca)003:1870: rnal 'byor ma rgyud thams cad kyi rtsa ba sangs
NK005(ca)003:1871: rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i lam 'di la
NK005(ca)003:1872: 'phags pa'i yul du bka' srol ji snyed cig mchis
NK005(ca)003:1873: pa las / phyogs 'dir yongs su grags pa ni
NK005(ca)003:1874: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dzas mdzad pa'i gsang don
NK005(ca)003:1875: rnam par bkod pa drug dang /
NK005(ca)003:1877: dbang chog rnams bsdoms pas nyams len gyi cha lag tshang ba gcig yin cing /
NK005(ca)003:1879: slob dpon h+aum k+aa ras mdzad pa'i he ru ka'i sgrub thabs dang /
NK005(ca)003:1880: yan lag bzhi'i snang ba dang /
NK005(ca)003:1881: dbang chog ste gsum bsdoms pas kyang cha tshang ba gcig go //
NK005(ca)003:1882: de gnyis nang gses phra mo'i khyad par las don gyi rkang gcig par snang zhing /
NK005(ca)003:1884: in+d+ra b+hu ti dang brgya byin sdong po'i 'grel chen sogs snga 'gyur dang /
NK005(ca)003:1885: kha che rin chen rdo rje'i dkyil chog sogs phyi 'gyur dang /
NK005(ca)003:1886: rong zom chen po'i rgyud 'grel sogs rgya bod kyi gzhung ji snyed pa las /
NK005(ca)003:1887: phyogs 'dir 'phel ba'i sgrub dkyil phal cher ku ku r+aa dza dang /
NK005(ca)003:1888: h+aum mdzad kyi gzhung rnams kyi rjes su 'brang yang /
NK005(ca)003:1889: gsar ma'i cho ga khrigs la bag chags brtags pas
NK005(ca)003:1890: de dag dang mthun par sbyar ba 'ba' zhig tu
NK005(ca)003:1891: snang bas / 'dir ni rtsa ba'i khungs nyid kyi
NK005(ca)003:1892: khrigs dngos shugs ci rigs pa las rnying ma rang
NK005(ca)003:1893: lugs kyi cho ga rnams dang babs gcig tu yod
NK005(ca)003:1894: snang bas / pas / de dang rigs mthun bka'
NK005(ca)003:1895: ma'i chog khrigs 'gros gcig pa rnams don la mi
NK005(ca)003:1896: 'gal zhing lag len 'jug pa bde ba'i dbang du
NK005(ca)003:1897: snang bas / pas / byas pa las / de
NK005(ca)003:1898: yang rigs rkyang gi dkyil 'khor tha dad du sgrub
NK005(ca)003:1899: pa ni skabs de dang der shes par 'gyur zhing
NK005(ca)003:1900: snang bas / pas / byas pa las / / rigs bsdus kyi dkyil 'khor 'god tshul la /
NK005(ca)003:1901: slob dpon in+d+ra b+hu tis rdor sems dbus su dang /
NK005(ca)003:1906: he ru ka steng khang du 'god par mdzad cing /
NK005(ca)003:1907: phyis dmar ston rgyal mtshan 'od zer gyis kyang phyag
NK005(ca)003:1908: len de ltar mdzad ces 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal
NK005(ca)003:1910: h+aum mdzad kyis rdor sems sogs rigs lnga'i sgo nas sngon du bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1911: he ru ka'i sgo nas sgrub pa bya ba yin pas /
NK005(ca)003:1912: de gnyis dus tha dad du bstan kyang gang zag
NK005(ca)003:1913: gi bye brag tu ma gyur pas thabs kyi cho
NK005(ca)003:1915: zhes rong zom chen po gsung ngo //
NK005(ca)003:1917: gzhi dkyil gcig gi nang du sgos dkyil drug po dbus su rdor sems /
NK005(ca)003:1922: byang shar du rta mchog 'god pa las bris dkyil
NK005(ca)003:1923: la yo srong cha snyoms pa bde mchog 'khor los
NK005(ca)003:1924: sgyur drug bzhin byed pas nyid la phyis kyi bla
NK005(ca)003:1925: ma rnams phyag len mdzad pa shas che'o //
NK005(ca)003:1927: 'ga' zhig he ru ka dbus dang /
NK005(ca)003:1928: rdor sems mthar bkod nas rigs bsdus la mnyam sbyor khro bo dang /
NK005(ca)003:1929: rdor sems rigs rkyang la zhi ba'i tha snyad byed pa mi legs so //
NK005(ca)003:1931: gtso bo 'pho ba'i dbang du byed na ni rnam
NK005(ca)003:1932: pa drug ka yang 'byung ste gur rigs bsdus bzhin
NK005(ca)003:1933: no // des na 'dir ni yan lag bzhi pa las /
NK005(ca)003:1934: nang gi dkyil 'khor dbyibs dag ni //
NK005(ca)003:1935: thig bzhi'i rnam par phye ba la //
NK005(ca)003:1936: so so'i pho brang ji lta bar //
NK005(ca)003:1937: rigs bsdus dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i tshul //
NK005(ca)003:1938: dbus su rigs bdag 'khor lo ste //
NK005(ca)003:1939: shar du de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
NK005(ca)003:1940: lho phyogs rdo rje drag po'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)003:1941: nub tu pad+ma rnam dag chos //
NK005(ca)003:1942: byang phyogs yon tan rin chen mdzod //
NK005(ca)003:1943: shar mtshams zhi dkyil sdud pa'i tshul //
NK005(ca)003:1944: lho mtshams drag po srid byed ltar //
NK005(ca)003:1945: nub mtshams dbang mdzad g.yo ba'i bzhin //
NK005(ca)003:1946: byang mtshams rgyas pa dbang chen ltar //
NK005(ca)003:1947: rang rang phreng bas mdzes par bya //
NK005(ca)003:1948: zhes pa ni gzhung 'di'i rtsa ba'i khungs nyid de /
NK005(ca)003:1949: de ltar bkod pa ni dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i lugs so //
NK005(ca)003:1951: rta mchog la dkyil 'khor gcig byas nas dkyil 'khor drug tu byed pa ni 'bring po'o //
NK005(ca)003:1953: lha dgu dgu'i nang gi dkyil 'khor kho na drug
NK005(ca)003:1954: bkod nas mchod lha dang sgo srung gzhi dkyil kho
NK005(ca)003:1955: na la bkod pa tsam gyis chog pa ni bsdus
NK005(ca)003:1956: pa'o // dkyil 'khor phyi nang thams cad la srung 'khor tshun dang /
NK005(ca)003:1957: rta babs dang bcas pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1959: gsum po yang de dang de la ltos pa'i rgyas 'bring bsdus pa'i tshul lo //
NK005(ca)003:1960: rta mchog gi lha 'god tshul ni /
NK005(ca)003:1961: dkyil 'khor dgu pa ltar na shar lho shar dang mtshungs pa sogs mi 'dra ba bzhi yin cing /
NK005(ca)003:1962: bzhi ka'ang rta mchog sgos kyi lha mo gnyis kyis lhag pa'o //
NK005(ca)003:1964: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i tshe na rta mchog gi 'khor
NK005(ca)003:1965: las dang rin chen phyogs mthun pa'i dbang gis rdo
NK005(ca)003:1966: rje nyi ma dang mtshungs par byas na zhi ba
NK005(ca)003:1967: dang / khro dkyil du byed na he ru ka'i bzhin te /
NK005(ca)003:1968: rta mchog khro bo gtso che bas de ltar byas na legs zhes gsung ngo //
NK005(ca)003:1971: gsang don rnam par bkod pa drug las rdor sems
NK005(ca)003:1972: la rgyu 'bras rdor 'dzin gyi dbye ba med cing
NK005(ca)003:1973: / rigs lhag ma lnga la rgyu rdor sems las
NK005(ca)003:1974: 'bras bu rdor 'dzin du skad cig gis bsgyur bar
NK005(ca)003:1975: / mdzad mod / de ni rgyu 'bras rdor 'dzin
NK005(ca)003:1976: thob thang yod med kyi dbye ba ma yin gyi
NK005(ca)003:1977: / mdzad mod / / gnyis ka rung ba'i shes byed do //
NK005(ca)003:1978: rigs rkyang la de ltar yin pa bzhin du rigs bsdus la yang go bar 'gyur ro //
NK005(ca)003:1980: rigs bsdus kyi skabs 'dir 'khor gyi lha mo rnams yab can du byed pa'ang yod mod /
NK005(ca)003:1981: 'on kyang de thams cad gtso bo nyid kyi shes rab mar byas na legs zhes gsung ngo //
NK005(ca)003:1983: mchod pa'i skabs su rigs rkyang he ru ka'i sgrub
NK005(ca)003:1984: thabs las rak+ta sogs khyad par gyi mchod pa rnams
NK005(ca)003:1985: bshad pas de dag rigs bsdus la don gyis thob
NK005(ca)003:1986: cing / gtor chog lhag gtor dang gnad gcig tu
NK005(ca)003:1987: byed pa yang rtsa ba'i khungs nyid kyis gsal por
NK005(ca)003:1988: cing / gsungs pa dang / der ma zad sgrub
NK005(ca)003:1989: thabs phyi ma rnams su ma bkod pa'i byin 'bebs
NK005(ca)003:1990: dang ting 'dzin gsum sogs snga 'gyur gyi gsang ba
NK005(ca)003:1991: spyi'i cho ga'i khyad chos rnams kyang /
NK005(ca)003:1992: gsang don dang h+aum mdzad kyi yan lag bzhi pa gsal bar gsungs pa dang /
NK005(ca)003:1993: brtan ma mchod pa'ang bod kyi phyogs 'dir dkar phyogs
NK005(ca)003:1994: kyi phrin las bsgrub pa la khyad par gyi dam
NK005(ca)003:1995: tshig mnos pas / mthu nus lhag par myur ba'i
NK005(ca)003:1996: phyir rdo rje slob dpon chen po rnams kyis yi
NK005(ca)003:1997: dam zhi khro'i cho ga thams cad dang rjes 'brel
NK005(ca)003:1998: du 'god par mdzad pas mtshon te rnying ma rang
NK005(ca)003:1999: lugs gang yin pa de dang mthun par 'gal med
NK005(ca)003:2000: du bkod pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)003:2001: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba zab mo'i dbyings //
NK005(ca)003:2002: bde chen ye shes rdo rjer mnyam sbyor bas //
NK005(ca)003:2003: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde ba'i mchog nyid de //
NK005(ca)003:2004: rnal 'byor ma rgyud kun gyi snying po'i phul //
NK005(ca)003:2005: shin tu rtogs daka'i rgyud don nam mkha'i mtha' //
NK005(ca)003:2006: 'phags mchog mkha' lding dbang po'i spyod yul las //
NK005(ca)003:2007: blo rmongs sbrang bus bgrod pas gzhal rlom pa //
NK005(ca)003:2008: smyon pa'i zlos gar nyid mtshungs de lta na'ang //
NK005(ca)003:2009: deng dus tshul 'dir don gnyer ches dkon zhing //
NK005(ca)003:2010: ming tsam 'dzin pa'ang rgya la rnyed daka'i phyir //
NK005(ca)003:2011: cung zad 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i rgyur dmigs nas //
NK005(ca)003:2012: lhag bsam kho nas gya tshom nyid du brjod //
NK005(ca)003:2013: 'on kyang rgya bod mkhas grub che rnams kyi //
NK005(ca)003:2014: gzhung 'grel phal cher zab barlinga rtogs dka' zhing //
NK005(ca)003:2015: phyogs 'dir spel ba'i sgrub dkyil 'ga' zhig kyang //
NK005(ca)003:2016: rang blo'i lam du rigs 'gres drangs par mthong //
NK005(ca)003:2017: de phyir snga 'gyur gzhung bzang rtsa ba yi //
NK005(ca)003:2018: khungs dang rjes 'brel dag gsal 'jug bde'i khrigs //
NK005(ca)003:2019: rgya che'i gzhung don 'khrul med mtshon byed pa //
NK005(ca)003:2020: gang 'di sngon goms skal bzang mthu las byung //
NK005(ca)003:2021: 'di las bsod nams gang zhig thob 'gyur des //
NK005(ca)003:2022: zab mo'i lam 'di 'phel zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK005(ca)003:2023: de las 'gro kun rigs drug dkyil 'khor lha'i //
NK005(ca)003:2024: bde chen dbyings su mnyam par sbyor gyur cig /
NK005(ca)003:2025: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba rigs bsdus pa'i
NK005(ca)003:2026: dkyil 'khor chen po'i sgrub thabs bde chen 'dod 'jo
NK005(ca)003:2028: deng dus zab mo'i lam 'di'i ming tsam 'dzin pa'ang
NK005(ca)003:2029: shin tu dkon par snang bas 'phel zhing mi nub
NK005(ca)003:2030: pa'i sgor 'gyur bar bsams nas slob dpon chen po
NK005(ca)003:2031: ku ku r+aa dza dang h+aum k+aa ra sogs kyi
NK005(ca)003:2032: gzhung rnams dang rong zom chen po'i rgyud 'grel sogs
NK005(ca)003:2033: legs par bshad pa rnams kyi rjes su 'brangs nas
NK005(ca)003:2034: / sh+aakya'i dge bsnyen rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med
NK005(ca)003:2035: rdo rjes dpa' bo zhes pa lcags 'brug khrums kyi
NK005(ca)003:2036: nya ba'i dus dge bar o rgyan smin grol gling
NK005(ca)003:2037: gi dge gnas su sbyar ba bde legs su gyur
